r%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20first%20information%20report%20(FIR)%20has%20been%20filed%20by%20Ganderbal%20police%20station%20under%20Section%2013%20(advocating%2C%20abetting%20or%20inciting%20any%20unlawful%20activity)%20of%20the%20Unlawful%20Activities%20Prevention%20Act%2C%201967%20(UAPA)%20and%20Sections%20505%20(inciting%20communal%20violence)%20and%20506%20(criminal%20intimidation)%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20said%20that%20the%20incident%20took%20place%20on%20November%2019%20at%20one%20of%20the%20two%20undergraduate%20hostels%20of%20the%20Sher-e-Kashmir%20University%20of%20Agriculture%20Science%20and%20Technology%20in%20the%20Ganderbal%20district%2C%20after%20India%20lost%20to%20Australia%20in%20the%20finals.%20They%20said%20that%20there%20was%20sloganeering%20allegedly%20inside%20the%20hostel%2C%20where%20some%20local%20students%20stay.%20The%20alleged%20slogan-shouting%20was%20filmed%20by%20non-local%20students%20and%20handed%20over%20to%20police.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20FIR%20was%20filed%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20a%20complaint%20by%20Sachin%20Bains%2C%20a%20student%20of%20the%20Faculty%20of%20Veterinary%20Science%20and%20Animal%20Husbandry%20at%20the%20university.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20suspects%20have%20been%20identified%20as%20Umer%2C%20Asif%2C%20Mohsin%2C%20Tauqeer%2C%20Khali%2C%20Sameer%2C%20and%20Ubaid%20Gulzar%20who%20are%20enrolled%20in%20different%20courses%20at%20the%20university.%20Most%20of%20them%20are%20believed%20to%20be%20on%20the%20verge%20of%20completing%20their%20degrees%2C%20officials%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20FIR%2C%20a%20copy%20of%20which%20is%20with%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20complainant%20told%20the%20police%20that%20he%20was%20allegedly%20abused%20and%20threatened%20by%20the%20students%20purportedly%20over%20rooting%20for%20India%20during%20the%20final%20of%20the%20World%20Cup%2C%20which%20was%20clinched%20by%20A