9ad%20Baker)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussia-college-students-asked-give-e-cigarettes-make-drones-report-2023-11%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'I%20was%20feeling%20bad'%3A%20Ishan%20on%20not%20getting%20enough%20chances%20in%20WC%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701090322000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-105537648%2Cimgsize-31716.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Faustralia-in-india%2Fi-was-feeling-a-bit-bad-ishan-kishan-on-not-getting-enough-chances-in-world-cup%2Farticleshow%2F105537589.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India's%20batsman%20Ishan%20Kishan%20conveyed%20his%20disappointment%20at%20missing%20multiple%20matches%20in%20the%20just-concluded%20ICC%20ODI%20World%20Cup%202023%20held%20in%20India.%20Despite%20this%20setback%2C%20he%20remained%20resolute%20in%20his%20determination%20to%20seize%20opportunities%20in%20the%20ensuing%20T20Is%2C%20motivated%20by%20a%20strong%20desire%20to%20showcase%20his%20performance.%20After%20the%20conclusion%20of%20the%20World%20Cup%2C%20Ishan%2C%20who%20featured%20in%20just%20two%20matches%20in%20the%20World%20Cup%2C%20scoring%2047%20runs%2C%20including%20a%20duck%2C%20was%20picked%20for%20the%20five-match%20T20I%20series%20against%20Australia.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20SPORTS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Analysis%3A%20Will%20Rythu%20Bandhu%20Pause%20Really%20Impact%20Telangana%20Votes%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20excitement%20of%20elections%20is%20all%20about%20the%20twists%20and%20turns%20in%20the%20run-up%20to%20voting%20day%2C%20which%20sometimes%20produce%20tectonic%20shifts%20and%20change%20the%20dynamics%20of%20the%20electoral%20battlefield.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BRS%20(Bharat%20Rashtra%20Samithi)%20had%20hoped%20that%20with%20the%20Election%20Commission%20giving%20the%20go-ahead%20to%20disburse%20money%20under%20the%20Rythu%20Bandhu%20scheme%2C%202023%20could%20become%20a%20repeat%20of%202018.%20The%20hope%20was%20that%20it%20would%20drive%20the%20outcome%20of%20the%20election%20and%20replicate%20a%202018%20repeat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20Election%20Commission%20has%20now%20stopped%20the%20transfer%20of%20money%20and%20the%20Congress%20is%20understandably%20elated%20as%20the%20BRS%20has%20lost%20a%20psychological%20advantage%20that%20could%20have%20accrued%20with%20the%20money%20pouring%20into%20accounts%20under%20the%20popular%20scheme.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20camp%20had%20feared%20that%20like%20in%202018%2C%20people%20would%20receive%20notifications%20on%20their%20phones%20of%20money%20deposited%20in%20their%20accounts%20even%20as%20they%20stood%20in%20line%20to%20vote.%20The%20feel-good%20factor%2C%20Congress%20leaders%20believe%2C%20helped%20the%20BRS.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIs%20the%20Election%20Commission's%20order%20a%20big%20setback%20to%20the%20BRS%3F%20Some%2066%20lakh%20farmers%20have%20enjoyed%20the%20benefit%20of%20the%20Rs%2072%2C000%20crore%20direct%20cash%20transfer%20over%2010-11%20cropping%20seasons.%20These%20farmers%20cultivated%20over%201.43%20crore%20acres%20and%20received%20Rs%205%2C000%20per%20acre%20per%20season.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Rabi%20amounts%20were%20to%20be%20paid%20out%20between%20October%20and%20January.%20So%2C%20there%20is%20no%20reason%20people%20would%20be%20unduly%20disappointed%20if%20the%20money%20is%20paused%20until%20November%2030.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20money%20is%20not%20unexpected%3B%20it%20has%20been%20paid%20out%20every%20season%2C%20ever%20since%20the%20Rythu%20Bandhu%20scheme%20came%20into%20effect%2C%20and%20a%20new%20instalment%20would%20have%20reinforced%20the%20credibility%20or%20dependability%20of%20the%20KCR%20government%20at%20a%20time%20when%20questions%20are%20being%20raised%20about%20whether%20the%20Congress%20can%20deliver%20on%20its%20lofty%20promises.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20the%20Election%20Commission%20had%20objected%20to%20was%20Telangana%20Finance%20Minister%20Harish%20Rao%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BYour%20mobile%20phones%20will%20start%20buzzing%20with%20the%20message%20that%20money%20has%20been%20transferred%20into%20your%20account%20on%20Tuesday%20morning%26quot%3B%20and%20adding%20that%20they%20should%20remember%20KCR%20(Chief%20Minister%20K%20Chandrasekhar%20Rao)%20was%20responsible%20for%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%20the%20BRS%20leaders%20are%20blaming%20Congress%20for%20the%20payouts%20to%20their%20accounts%20being%20stopped%2C%20telling%20farmers%20that%20the%20party%20is%20anti-farmer.%20They%20are%20also%20telling%20people%20the%20Congress%20will%20give%20them%20only%20Rs%2015%2C000%20annually%2C%20whatever%20the%20size%20of%20their%20land%20holding%2C%20compared%20to%20the%20BRS%20distributing%20Rs%2010%2C000%20per%20acre%2C%20with%20the%20promise%20of%20increasing%20it%20to%20Rs%2016%2C000%20per%20acre%20in%20stages.%20Not%20a%20word%20about%20tenant%20farmers%20or%20agricultural%20labourers%2C%20who%20are%20not%20covered%20under%20the%20scheme.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20Congress%20leader%20Revanth%20Reddy%20is%20telling%20farmers%20that%20Harish%20Rao%20is%20responsible%20for%20stopping%20the%20Rythu%20Bandhu%20transfers%20to%20their%20accounts.%20The%20party%20leaders%20continue%20to%20tell%20people%20that%20the%20Congress's%20schemes%20for%20farmers%20include%20tenant%20farmers%2C%20who%20comprise%2036%20per%20cent%20of%20cultivators.%20The%20party%20has%20also%20promised%20to%20pay%20Rs%2012%2C000%20annually%20to%20agriculture%20labourers%20and%20also%20waive%20crop%20loans%20of%20up%20to%20Rs%202%20lakh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20is%20not%20focusing%20on%20criticism%20that%20the%20most%20landed%2C%20richest%20farmers%20are%20drawing%20the%20maximum%20benefit%20from%20among%20the%2066%20lakh%20beneficiaries%20of%20the%20Rythu%20Bandhu%20scheme.%20In%20election%20season%2C%20you%20cannot%20afford%20to%20alienate%20anyone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUndoubtedly%2C%20the%20Opposition%20Congress%20made%20the%20maximum%20gains%20in%20the%20last%20few%20weeks%20and%20months%2C%20with%20a%20visible%20momentum%20building%20up%20for%20the%20party.%20That%20was%20a%20swing%20in%20the%20public%20mood%20that%20the%20BRS%20was%20unable%20to%20control.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20too%20has%20been%20dismissed%20as%20a%20non-player%20but%20they%20too%20will%20make%20significant%20gains%20in%20vote%20share%20and%20the%20number%20of%20seats.%20Just%20the%20Prime%20Minister's%20roadshows%2C%20public%20meetings%20and%20street%20corner%20meetings%20of%20Amit%20Shah%20and%20others%20could%20add%20a%20neat%202-3%20per%20cent%20vote%20share%20advantage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20now%20is%20the%20time%20for%20the%20BRS%20to%20play%20its%20Brahmastra%20or%20ultimate%20weapon.%20Senior%20leaders%20and%20even%20the%20Opposition%20admit%20that%20KCR's%20ability%20to%20cover%20the%20last%20mile%20and%20reach%20the%20last%20voter%20is%20impressive.%20The%20well-entrenched%20networks%20of%20the%20BRS%20party%20will%20be%20at%20work%20to%20ensure%20unofficial%20benefits%20reach%20in%20hand%20and%20turn%20the%20last-minute%20sentiment%20and%20the%20votes%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20big%20advantage%20for%20the%20ruling%20party%20is%20that%20all%20its%20campaign%20managers%20are%20locals%2C%20district%20and%20mandal%20leaders%2C%20whereas%20at%20many%20places%2C%20for%20the%20Congress%20and%20even%20the%20BJP%2C%20the%20managers%20are%20imported%20from%20outside%20-%20for%20example%20Karnataka%20-%20and%20would%20be%20expected%20to%20leave%20the%20constituency%20on%20the%20eve%20of%20election.%20So%20they%20are%20unable%20to%20connect%20with%20the%20pulse%20of%20voters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20happened%20just%20before%20the%20Munugode%20bypolls%20too.%20Add%20to%20this%20the%20effective%20use%20of%20social%20media%20networks%20to%20create%20negative%20propaganda%20of%20unfulfilled%20expectations%20for%20the%20opponent.%20One%20strategist%20directly%20involved%20in%20the%20operation%20admitted%20it%20was%20time%20for%20dirty%20tricks.%20Put%20out%20the%20word%20that%20the%20opposition%20candidate%20and%20party%20are%2C%20for%20example%2C%20doing%203X%20for%20the%20voter%20whereas%20the%20voter%20may%20only%20receive%20X.%20That%20creates%20discontent%2C%20frustration%20and%20disappointment%20in%20that%20candidate%20and%20party%2C%20benefitting%20the%20rival%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEvery%20party%20is%20in%20the%20game.%20The%20difference%20is%20in%20how%20smoothly%20and%20efficiently%20they%20carry%20out%20the%20operation.%20Perhaps%20that%20is%20why%20Revanth%20Reddy%20likened%20fighting%20an%20election%20to%20art.%20%26quot%3BTill%20the%20last%20stroke%2C%20you%20may%20not%20know%20what%20the%20painting%20is%20going%20to%20be.%20Nothing%20different%20about%20an%20election.%26quot%3B%20The%20man%20formally%20trained%20to%20be%20a%20visual%20art%20student%20should%20know.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHoping%20for%20a%20last-minute%20twist%20to%20the%20Rythu%20Bandhu%20story%2C%20the%20BRS%20has%20written%20to%20the%20Election%20Commission%20saying%20there%20was%20no%20violation%20of%20the%20model%20code%20and%20requesting%20that%20the%20decision%20be%20reversed.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701090300000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Fn08li8m4_brs-party-generic-1200_625x300_09_November_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fanalysis-will-rythu-bandhu-pause-really-impact-telangana-votes-4610762%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20excitement%20of%20elections%20is%20all%20about%20the%20twists%20and%20turns%20in%20the%20run-up%20to%20voting%20day%2C%20which%20sometimes%20produce%20tectonic%20shifts%20and%20change%20the%20d