s%20not%20anti-Hindi%20but%20opposed%20to%20diminishing%20Tamil%20and%20Tamil%20identity%20to%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%98%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eregional%20language%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%99%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eor%20concern.%20V.P.%20Singh%20was%20a%20prime%20minister%2C%20but%20the%20pitch%20to%20catapult%20a%20Hindi-belt%20icon%20for%20backwards%2C%20best%20known%20for%20dusting%20off%20the%20Mandal%20report%20recommendations%20and%20implementing%20them%2C%20much%20to%20the%20BJP%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%99%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Es%20chagrin%20at%20the%20time%2C%20has%20its%20significance.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EThird%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20V.P.%20Singh%20being%20lauded%20for%20the%20social%20justice%20revolution%20in%20north%20India%20could%20also%20be%20read%20as%20a%20subtle%20message%20to%20the%20Congress%20party%20%E2%80%93%20that%20their%20recent%20embrace%20of%20social%20justice%2C%20does%20not%20mean%20they%20have%20full%20control%20about%20how%20to%20power%20that%20message.%20Drawing%20in%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%2C%20who%20has%20been%20vocal%20about%20not%20getting%20what%20he%20thinks%20is%20his%20due%20from%20Congress%20in%20terms%20of%20seats%20in%20the%20recent%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20polls%20could%20be%20seen%20as%20an%20overture%20to%20a%20fellow-INDIAn%2C%20but%20also%20as%20a%20not-so-subtle%20message%20to%20Congress%2C%20that%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20is%20to%20be%20projected%20as%20a%20big%20leader%2C%20and%20kept%20inside%20the%20tent.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EFourth%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%99%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Es%20father%20%E2%80%93%20Samajwadi%20Party%20founder%20and%20stalwart%2C%20the%20late%20Mulayam%20Singh%20Yadav%20%E2%80%93%20was%20seen%20as%20a%20bitter%20rival%20of%20VP%20Singh%2C%20having%20cast%20his%20lot%20with%20another%20socialist%20giant%20and%20former%20PM%2C%20Chandrashekhar.%20So%20for%20Akhilesh%20too%2C%20th