20Sunday%2C%20five%20days%20after%20chief%20minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmailtrack.io%2Flink%2F8eeba777182f7c8ac6542a4505c275c8762cc43e%3Furl%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fthewire.in%252Fpolitics%252Fmystery-around-mamata-banerjees-fresh-investment-call-for-tajpur-port-assigned-to-adani-a-year-ago%26userId%3D7302199%26signature%3D42375cb9c0250b3e%5C%22%3Egave%20a%20fresh%20investment%20call%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20the%20Rs%2025%2C000%20crore%20project%20at%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20flagship%20business%20event%2C%20Bengal%20Global%20Business%20Summit%20(BGBS).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20proposed%20first%20deep%20sea%20port%20at%20Tajpur%20is%20ready.%20You%20can%20participate%20in%20the%20tender.%20It%20will%20attract%20an%20investment%20of%20about%20%243%20billion%2C%20meaning%20Rs%2025%2C000%20crore%2C%E2%80%9D%20Banerjee%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20journalists%20asked%20Panja%20if%20her%20statement%20contradicted%20that%20of%20the%20chief%20minister%2C%20she%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20am%20speaking%20on%20behalf%20of%20the%20honourable%20chief%20minister.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdani%20Port%20and%20Special%20Economic%20Zone%20(APSEZ)%20head%20Karan%20Adani%20received%20a%20Letter%20of%20Intent%20from%20the%20state%20government%20in%20October%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20lack%20of%20consistency%20between%20the%20statements%20of%20the%20state%20government%20and%20the%20Adani%20Group%20regarding%20the%20status%20of%20the%20projects%20over%20the%20past%20few%20months%20has%20given%20rise%20to%20speculation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20state%20government%20had%20on%20several%20occasions%20said%20they%20were%20waiting%20for%20the%20Adani%20Group%20to%20do%20their%20part%20regarding%20necessary%20permissions%20from%20the%20Union%20government%2C%20the%20Adani%20Group%20had%20said%20at%20least%20three%20times%20that%20they%20were%20awaiting%20the%20Letter%20of%20Award%20(LoA)%20from%20the%20government%20to%20start%20with%20the%20other%20processes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20chief%20minister%E2%80%99s%20surprise%20announcement%20on%20November%2021%20prompted%20many%20to%20speculate%20if%20this%20was%20the%20fallout%20of%20a%20political%20tussle%20between%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20and%20Mamata%20Banerjee%E2%80%99s%20Trinamool%20Congress%20(TMC)%20involving%20the%20latter%E2%80%99s%20MP%20Mahua%20Moitra%E2%80%99s%20allegedly%20anti-Adani%E2%80%99s%20interests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBanerjee%E2%80%99s%20public%20backing%20of%20Moitra%20the%20very%20next%20day%20strengthened%20the%20speculations.%20%E2%80%9CWhat%20she%20(Moitra)%20used%20to%20say%20inside%2C%20she%20will%20not%20be%20saying%20outside%2C%E2%80%9D%20Banerjee%20had%20said%20at%20a%20party%20event.%20Moitra%20is%20known%20for%20regularly%20accusing%20the%20Modi%20government%20of%20giving%20undue%20favours%20to%20the%20Adani%20Group%20as%20part%20of%20a%20nexus.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20Banerjee%E2%80%99s%20call%20for%20participation%20in%20the%20tender%2C%20senior%20BJP%20leaders%20in%20the%20state%2C%20including%20Lok%20Sabha%20MP%20Dilip%20Ghosh%2C%20alleged%20that%20it%20was%20the%20Adani%20Group%20that%20backed%20out%20of%20the%20project%20because%20of%20Moitra%E2%80%99s%20role.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Sunday%2C%20Panja%20said%2C%20reading%20out%20from%20a%20written%20statement%2C%20that%20the%20Adani%20group%20was%20%E2%80%9Cgiven%20a%20provisional%20LoI%E2%80%9D%20and%20that%20the%20work%20for%20getting%20permissions%20required%20from%20the%20Union%20government%20ministries%20like%20shipping%2C%20home%2C%20defence%20and%20external%20affairs%20%E2%80%9Care%20on.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Ministry%20of%20Home%20Affairs%20has%20given%20a%20conditional%20security%20clearance%20and%20has%20made%20some%20observations.%20We%20are%20working%20with%20the%20Adani%20Group%20regarding%20those%20observations%20and%20have%20asked%20for%20some%20clarifications.%20These%20communications%20are%20going%20on%20currently%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fbengali.abplive.com%2Fvideos%2Fdistrict%2Ftmc-leader-sashi-panja-said-talks-are-going-on-with-adani-about-building-a-port-at-tajpur-1027030%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20absence%20of%20the%20Adani%20Group%20at%20the%20BGBS%20triggered%20speculations%20over%20whether%20the%20group%20had%20%E2%80%9Csnubbed%E2%80%9D%20the%20government%20because%20of%20the%20ruling%20party%E2%80%99s%20political%20attacks%20alleging%20a%20%E2%80%9Cnexus%E2%80%9D%20between%20the%20business%20group%20and%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Panja%20asserted%20that%20the%20government%20had%20sent%20invites%20to%20the%20group%20for%20the%20business%20summit%2C%20a%20senior%20government%20official%2C%20who%20was%20unwilling%20to%20be%20identified%2C%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CInvite%20was%20sent%20as%20part%20of%20formality.%20The%20extra%20efforts%20that%20we%20usually%20make%20to%20ensure%20top%20industrialists%E2%80%99%20presence%20were%20not%20made%20for%20the%20Adani%20Group%20this%20year.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20Panja%E2%80%99s%20announcement%2C%20CPI(M)%20central%20committee%20member%20Sujan%20Chakraborty%20took%20potshots%20at%20the%20government.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20statements%20of%20Panja%20and%20the%20chief%20minister%20are%20contradictory.%20They%20(the%20TMC)%20are%20sometimes%20speaking%20up%20against%20Adani%20to%20hide%20their%20own%20nexus.%20But%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day%2C%20she%20(Banerjee)%20cannot%20go%20beyond%20what%20Delhi%20(BJP)%20tells%20her%20to%20do%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F20132022%2FAdani-arena.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F20132022%2FAdani-arena.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F20132022%2FAdani-arena-300x150.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F20132022%2FAdani-arena-1024x512.jpg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F20132022%2FAdani-arena-800x400.jpg%20800w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-664107%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EAn%20Adani%20building%20in%20Australia.%20Representative%20image.%20Photo%3A%20Wikimedia%20Commons%2FRegionalQueenslander%2C%20CC%20BY-SA%204.0.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3E%E2%80%98Important%20for%20both%E2%80%99%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Kolkata-based%20business%20and%20political%20observers%2C%20the%20Tajpur%20port%20project%20is%20important%20to%20both%20the%20state%20government%20as%20well%20as%20the%20Adani%20Group.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20the%20biggest%20industrial%20project%20the%20state%20government%20has%20taken%20up%20during%20Mamata%20Banerjee%E2%80%99s%2012-year%20rule%20%E2%80%93%20along%20with%20the%20proposed%20coal%20mine%20at%20Deucha-Pachami%20%E2%80%93%20but%20the%20work%20related%20to%20Tajpur%20port%20has%20progressed%20more%20than%20the%20coal%20mine%20project.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%2C%20to%20smoothen%20the%20process%20of%20the%20port%20development%2C%20had%20also%20scrapped%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20only%20proposed%20solar%20project%20%E2%80%93%20the%20Rs%20750%20crore%20project%20to%20develop%20a%20125-megawatt%20(MW)%20capacity%20solar%20park.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20state%20had%20received%20Rs%2025%20lakh%20from%20the%20Union%20government%20for%20preparing%20a%20detailed%20project%20report%20for%20the%20solar%20park.%20The%20report%20was%20complete%20and%20the%20process%20of%20securing%20an%20international%20loan%20had%20progressed.%20However%2C%20in%202021%2C%20the%20state%20government%20decided%20to%20prioritise%20the%20Tajpur%20project%20and%20handed%20over%20the%20532-acre%20plot%20at%20Dadanpatrabar%20earmarked%20for%20the%20solar%20park%20to%20the%20Tajpur%20port%20project.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20has%20also%20expedited%20the%20development%20of%20industrial%20corridors%2C%20including%20one%20from%20Tajpur%20to%20Dankuni%20near%20Kolkata.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20concession%20agreements%20being%20signed%20between%20governments%20and%20private%20industries%20for%20the%20development%2C%20operation%20and%20maintenance%20of%20different%20new%20ports%20and%20terminals%20in%20the%20country%20are%20usually%20for%20a%20period%20of%2030%20years%2C%20whereas%20in%20some%20cases%20a%20period%20of%20up%20to%2050%20years%20is%20being%20considered.%20The%20Adani%20Group%20had%20in%20August%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.moneycontrol.com%2Fnews%2Fbusiness%2Fadani-ports-for-minimum-50yrs-of-concession-period-in-ppp-projects-11186601.html%5C%22%3Eargued%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20favour%20of%2050-year%20concession%20periods.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20that%20context%2C%20the%2099-year%20concession%20period%20offered%20by%20the%20state%20government%20%E2%80%9Cis%20lucrative%2C%E2%80%9D%20according%20to%20a%20senior%20business%20journalist%20who%20did%20not%20want%20to%20be%20named.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdani%20Port%E2%80%99s%20brochure%20published%20in%20August%202023%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.adani.com%2F-%2Fmedia%2FProject%2FAdani%2Fdownloads%2FAdani-Ports-Brochure-August-2023.pdf%3Fla%3Den%26hash%3DA13AB50213B3EEBA948CF1FFA6A91280%5C%22%3Ehighlighted%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%2099-year%20concession%20given%20in%20Tajpur%20port%20development%20was%20the%20first%20instance%20in%20India.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Adanis%20hurriedly%20pulling%20out%20of%20such%20a%20project%20out%20of%20a%20political%20controversy%20does%20not%20make%20sense%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20journalist%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Adani%20Group%20bagged%20the%20LoI%20after%20emerging%20as%20the%20highest%20bidder%2C%20defeating%20another%20major%20business%20group%2C%20JSW.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20senior%20bureaucrat%20said%2C%20requesting%20anonymity%2C%20that%20the%20chief%20minister%E2%80%99s%20announcement%20was%20%E2%80%9Cshocking%20and%20surprising%E2%80%9D%20as%20there%20was%20no%20hint%20of%20such%20a%20measure%20even%20a%20day%20before.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20chief%20minister%20may%20have%20been%20upset%20that%20no%20one%20from%20the%20Adanis%20came%20to%20give%20updates%20on%20the%20project.%20But%20I%20totally%20understand%20if%20the%20Adanis%20did%20not%20send%20any%20representative%20to%20avoid%20being%20asked%20by%20the%20press%20on%20the%20Mahua%20Moitra%20episode%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20bureaucrat%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenior%20journalist%20Avijit%20Ghosal%2C%20however%2C%20suspects%20the%20chief%20minister%20may%20have%20miscommunicated%20what%20she%20intended%20to%20convey%20on%20November%2021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMega%20infrastructure%20projects%20like%20this%20do%20not%20happen%20overnight%20and%20the%20LoI%20is%20nearly%20the%20beginning%20of%20a%20very%20long%20drawn%20process%20of%20negotiations%20and%20a%20string%20of%20agreements%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20chief%20minister%20should%20have%20clarified%20her%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhat%20the%20chief%20minister%20may%20have%20meant%20is%20that%20while%20the%20Adanis%20remain%20the%20anchor%20investor%20in%20this%20project%2C%20there%20would%20be%20multiple%20sub-projects%20with%20wide%20investment%20opportunities%20for%20India%20Inc.%20She%20probably%20invited%20other%20industrial%20houses%20for%20wider%20investment.%20What%20she%20perhaps%20omitted%20was%20providing%20an%20explanation%20for%20her%20one-line%20statement.%20That%E2%80%99s%20the%20explanation%20that%20the%20state%20industries%20minister%20is%20providing%20now%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Ghosal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Adani%20Group%20will%20invest%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Findia%2Fcommitted-to-tajpur-port-waiting-for-formalities-from-bengal-govt-adani-official%2Farticleshow%2F97844349.cms%5C%22%3ERs%2015%2C000%20crore%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20project%2C%20while%20the%20associated%20infrastructural%20development%20cost%20has%20been%20projected%20at%20another%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.uniindia.com%2F~%2Fadani-port-receives-loi-for-tajpur-from-mamata-govt%2FStates%2Fnews%2F2840789.html%5C%22%3ERs%2010%2C000%20crore%3C%2Fa%3E.%20On%20November%2021%2C%20the%20chief%20minister%20mentioned%20Tajpur%20as%20a%20Rs%2025%2C000%20crore%20project.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701089107000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F04121914%2FF6AYMqwXkAAlspp.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fadani-group-tajpur-port-bengal-government-u-turn-mystery%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Five%20days%20after%20chief%20minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%E2%80%99s%20fresh%20investment%20call%2C%20industries%20minister%20Shashi%20Panka%20said%20discussions%20with%20Adani%20are%20continuing.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fadani-group-tajpur-port-bengal-government-u-turn-mystery%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20president%20of%20Lyft%20shares%20how%20learned%20to%20trust%20her%20instincts%20%E2%80%94%20and%20the%20Taylor%20Swift%20song%20she%20listens%20to%20before%20difficult%20meetings%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Kristin%20Sverchek%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65561cce36d588dc55d15e46%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EKristin%20Sverchek%3Cp%3ELyft%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EAfter%2011%20years%20at%20Lyft%2C%20Kristen%C2%A0Sverchek%20stepped%20into%20the%20president's%20role%20earlier%20this%20year.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIn%20the%20latest%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcategory%2Fthe-equity-talk%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EEquity%20Talk%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20she%20frequently%20asks%20herself%3A%20%26quot%3BIf%20I%20were%20a%20man%2C%20how%20would%20I%20handle%20this%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EShe%20has%20Slacked%20senior%20women%20leaders%20%26quot%3BThe%20Man%26quot%3B%20by%20Taylor%20Swift%20as%20a%20reminder%20of%C2%A0%26quot%3Byou%20got%20this.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ELyft's%20Kristen%20Sverchek%20has%20been%20with%20the%20ride-hailing%20company%20for%2011%20years%20this%20month%2C%20and%20she's%20seen%20the%20company%20built%20from%20the%20ground%20up.%20She%20was%20its%20first%20general%20counsel%2C%20helped%20take%20the%20company%20public%2C%20and%20was%20named%20president%20this%20July.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20been%20so%20fulfilling%20for%20me%20getting%20to%20flex%20different%20muscles%2C'%26quot%3B%20Sverchek%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BDavid%20%5BRisher%2C%20the%20new%20CEO%5D%2C%20has%20taken%20a%20more%20customer-obsessed%20lens%20to%20the%20business%2C%20and%20that's%20been%20really%20fun%20to%20be%20able%20to%20be%20on%20that%20journey%20with%20him%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOf%20course%2C%20working%20in%20male-dominated%20fields%20of%20tech%20and%20law%20isn't%20easy%2C%20and%20particularly%20in%20her%20early%20days%20as%20a%20lawyer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20often%20the%20only%20woman%20in%20the%20room%20and%20it%20could%20be%20hard%20to%20find%20my%20voice%20as%20a%20young%20woman%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20took%20a%20lot%20of%20grit%20and%20resilience%20and%20and%20it%20took%20me%20challenging%20myself%20to%20speak%20up%20even%20when%20I%20didn't%20feel%20comfortable.%20There's%20a%20there's%20a%20sort%20of%20thing%20that%20my%20husband%20and%20I%20say%20to%20each%20other%2C%20which%20is%20'If%20I%20were%20a%20man%2C%20how%20would%20I%20handle%20this%3F'%20And%20so%20sometimes%20it%20helps%20me%20to%20apply%20that%20rubric%20to%20a%20situation%2C%26quot%3B%20Sverchek%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20she's%20gotten%20more%20comfortable%20using%20her%20voice%20over%20the%20years%2C%20despite%20certain%20leadership%20muscles%20being%20%26quot%3Bhard%20to%20develop.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20following%20interview%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAs%20you%20learn%20who%20the%20Lyft%20customer%20is%2C%20what%20do%20you%20want%20to%20change%20and%20make%20better%20for%20them%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20think%20one%20of%20the%20things%20%E2%80%94%20which%20sounds%20really%20simple%2C%20but%20that%20we%20needed%20to%20do%20more%20of%20%E2%80%94%20was%20just%20listen%20to%20what%20our%20customers%20were%20asking%20for.%20And%20so%20you%20know%2C%20one%20of%20the%20one%20of%20the%20results%20of%20that%20listening%20was%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.lyft.com%2Fwomen%2B%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWomen%2B%20Connect%3C%2Fa%3E%20matching%20platform%20that%20we%20launched%20just%20about%20two%20months%20ago.%20We%20were%20hearing%20both%20from%20riders%20and%20drivers%20who%20are%20women%20that%20gee%2C%20%26quot%3BI'd%20really%20love%20to%20be%20matched%20with%20another%20woman%26quot%3B%20and%20from%20our%20non-binary%20users%20that%20they'd%20like%20to%20be%20matched%20with%20another%20non%20binary%20person.%20That%20was%20one%20of%20the%20first%20initiatives%20that%20David%20really%20pushed%20us%20on%20when%20he%20started%20as%20CEO.%20It%20was%20something%20that%20we%20were%20proud%20to%20be%20able%20to%20fully%20create%20from%20scratch%20and%20launch%20within%20like%20a%20four%20to%20five%20month%20period.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIn%20a%20male-dominated%20industry%20and%20sector%2C%20and%20maybe%20even%20company%2C%20how%20have%20you%20ensured%20your%20own%20career%20growth%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20hasn't%20been%20easy.%20And%20you%20know%2C%20that's%20true%20of%20tech%2C%20obviously%2C%20writ%20large%2C%20I%20think.%20Thankfully%2C%20at%20Lyft%2C%20we%20are%20in%2C%20I%20would%20say%20a%20good%20position%20of%20having%20nearly%20half%20of%20our%20director%20and%20above%20employees%20be%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20certainly%2C%20particularly%20in%20the%20early%20days%20of%20my%20career%20as%20a%20corporate%20attorney%2C%20I%20was%20often%20the%20only%20woman%20in%20the%20room%20and%20it%20could%20be%20hard%20to%20find%20my%20voice%20as%20a%20young%20woman%20especially.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20would%20say%20it%20took%20a%20lot%20of%20grit%20and%20resilience%20and%20and%20it%20took%20me%20challenging%20myself%20to%20speak%20up%20even%20when%20I%20didn't%20feel%20comfortable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESometimes%20my%20best%20friend%20and%20I%20joke%20around%20about%20%26quot%3Bacting%20like%20a%20white%20man%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3Cstrong%3E%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20really%20say%2C%20%26quot%3BHave%20the%20courage%20of%20a%20mediocre%20white%20male.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ELet's%20talk%20leadership%20lessons.%20Is%20there%20moment%20when%20you%20felt%20passed%20over%2C%20not%20listened%20to%2C%20and%20how%20did%20you%20overcome%20it%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20really%20hard%20to%20define%20one%20moment%20but%20I%20will%20say%20sort%20of%20an%20overarching%20thing%20and%20part%20of%20what's%20kept%20me%20at%20Lyft%20is%20that%20knowledge%20and%20understanding%20that%20the%20grass%20isn't%20necessarily%20greener%20elsewhere.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEspecially%20in%20the%20early%20days%20as%20general%20counsel%2C%20you%20know%2C%20this%20is%20a%20new%20and%20disruptive%20industry%20%E2%80%94%20we%20created%20the%20category%20of%20ride-sharing%20and%20so%20a%20lot%20of%20the%20legal%20advice%20that%20I%20was%20giving%20at%20the%20time%20was%20really%20me%20using%20my%20best%20common%20sense%20judgment.%20But%20there%20wasn't%20a%20lot%20of%20historical%20precedent%20for%20what%20I%20was%20advising%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20there%20were%20times%20where%20I'd%20have%20to%20take%20really%20a%20leap%20of%20faith%3A%20Is%20this%20the%20right%20judgment%20call%20with%20being%20questioned%20from%20all%20angles%20about%20whether%20we%20were%20doing%20the%20right%20thing%3F%20And%20really%20just%20having%20the%20courage%20and%20grit%20to%20stick%20by%20my%20guns%20when%20I%20knew%20that%20something%20was%20right.%20And%20now%20that%20we've%20seen%20many%2C%20many%20years%20pass%20in%20the%20industry%2C%20validating%20that%20many%20decisions%20over%20the%20years%20were%2C%20in%20fact%2C%20the%20right%20ones.%20So%20it%20was%20for%20me%20less%20of%20a%20moment%20and%20more%20of%20slow%20and%20steady%20over%20the%20years%20learning%20to%20trust%20my%20instinct.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20is%20the%20biggest%20challenge%20that%20you're%20seeing%20as%20a%20female%20leader%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELyft%20had%20a%20very%20tough%20few%20years.%20With%20COVID%2C%20folks%20stopped%20riding%20and%20we've%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapnews.com%2Farticle%2Flyft-ride-hailing-new-ceo-81d5b381a1e76e1c64915541375ebc83%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20leadership%20transition%3C%2Fa%3E.%20And%20so%20right%20now%2C%20really%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20what%20I%20think%20about%20is%20getting%20us%20back%20to%20our%20bearings%2C%20getting%20us%20back%20to%20our%20roots.%20We've%20had%20to%20make%20a%20lot%20of%20tough%20decisions%20over%20the%20last%20few%20years%20and%20now%20we're%20in%20a%20moment%20of%20stability%2C%20and%20we've%20got%20to%20preserve%20that%20moment%20of%20stability.%20That's%20a%20lot%20of%20what%20I%20think%20about%2C%20certainly%20with%20respect%20to%20being%20a%20woman%20in%20leadership%2C%20particularly%20it's%20making%20sure%20that%20the%20bench%20of%20women%20leaders%20goes%20deep%20down%20into%20the%20organization.%20So%20that%20if%20other%20women%20leave%2C%20we%20are%20not%20all%20of%20a%20sudden%20upside-down%20in%20terms%20of%20having%20a%20great%20slate%20of%20diversity%20at%20the%20company%20to%20lead%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDo%20you%20have%20a%20mantra%20you%20tell%20yourself%20before%20going%20into%20a%20difficult%20meeting%20or%20situation%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20less%20of%20a%20mantra%20and%20more%20of%20a%20song.%20It%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DAqAJLh9wuZ0%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Man%26quot%3B%20by%20Taylor%20Swift%3C%2Fa%3E.%20If%20you%20have%20listened%20to%20it%2C%20you%20will%20know%20it%20will%20pump%20you%20right%20up%20and%20about%20once%20a%20year%2C%20I'll%20Slack%20it%20to%20some%20of%20our%20senior%20leaders%2C%20women%20leaders%20at%20Lyft%2C%20as%20'%26quot%3Bhey%20you%20guys%20got%20this.%26quot%3B%20For%20me%2C%20if%20I%20really%20need%20to%20be%20psyched%20up%2C%20I'm%20going%20to%20listen%20to%20that%20song.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20are%20you%20setting%20examples%20for%20young%20leaders%20and%20workers%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20probably%20two%20things%20I%20would%20say.%20One%20is%20that%20I%20try%20to%20help%20people%20wherever%20I%20can.%20So%20if%20somebody%20reaches%20out%20to%20me%20and%20they%20want%20an%20introduction%20or%20somebody%20reaches%20out%20to%20me%20and%20they%20want%20a%20piece%20of%20advice%2C%20I%20always%20try%20to%20make%20time%20and%20space%20for%20that%20person%2C%20even%20if%20I%20don't%20know%20how%20I'm%20going%20to%20be%20able%20to%20help%20them.%20I%20make%20time%20and%20I%20do%20what%20I%20can.%20I%20think%20of%20all%20of%20the%20people%20through%20the%20years%20who%20made%20time%20for%20me%20for%20a%20coffee%2C%20for%20a%20phone%20call%2C%20etc.%20And%20that's%20something%20that%20I%20feel%20is%20really%20important%20to%20pay%20forward.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20an%20example%2C%20just%20last%20week%2C%20hosted%20probably%20about%2020%20women%2C%20law%20students%20from%20Berkeley%20Law%2C%20which%20is%20where%20I%20went%20to%20undergrad%20who%20did%20a%20Q%26amp%3BA%20with%20me%2C%20as%20well%20as%20our%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fin%2Flindsayllewellyn%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGeneral%20Counsel%20Lindsay%20Llewellyn%2C%20%3C%2Fa%3Ewho%20is%20also%20a%20woman.%20And%20so%20really%20just%20helping%20them%20to%20see%20representation%20of%20women%20and%20leadership%20at%20a%20tech%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20other%20thing%20I%20was%20going%20to%20mention%2C%20which%20is%20kind%20of%20going%20back%20several%20years%20now%2C%20is%20when%20I%20started%20at%20Lyft%20we%20were%20such%20a%20small%20company%20and%20such%20a%20young%20company%20that%20we%20hadn't%20had%20any%20women%20take%20maternity%20leave.%20So%20I%20was%20the%20first%20one%20to%20create%20the%20policy%20and%20to%20go%20out%20on%20leave.%20This%20was%20way%20back%20in%20January%20of%202015.%20And%20the%20biggest%20thing%20that%20I%20did%20in%20that%20moment%2C%20which%20was%20with%20a%20helpful%20push%20from%20one%20of%20our%20board%20members%2C%20was%20take%20the%20entire%20maternity%20leave%20and%20thereby%20set%20the%20example%20that%20it%20was%20not%20just%20acceptable%20%E2%80%94%20but%20encouraged%20%E2%80%94%20for%20other%20women%2C%20and%20men%20by%20the%20way%20to%20do%20this.%20Because%20our%20policy%20is%20equal%20for%20moms%20and%20dads%20and%20adoptive%20parents.%20That%20was%20something%20that%20was%20important%20to%20me%20when%20I%20had%20that%20first%20child%20and%202015%20but%20then%20as%20I%20had%20my%20second%20third%20kids%20through%20the%20years%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20really%20hard%20for%20me%20honestly%20at%20that%20time%20to%20imagine%20not%20being%20at%20work.%20Our%20policy%20is%20about%20four-and-a-half%20months%20long.%20And%20I'm%20just%20one%20of%20these%20people%20who's%20worked%20since%20I%20was%2016.%20And%20so%20I%20actually%20couldn't%20really%20imagine%20not%20working%20for%20that%20long%20of%20a%20period%20of%20time.%20But%20I%20absolutely%20needed%20the%20time.%20Being%20a%20parent%20to%20a%20newborn%20is%20no%20small%20task.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20is%20the%20most%20common%20topic%20of%20conversation%20you%20find%20yourself%20pulled%20into%20in%20the%20hallways%20at%20Lyft%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E(Sverchek%20goes%20into%20the%20office%20three%20days%20a%20week.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20actually%20don't%20know%20how%20to%20answer%20what%20the%20most%20common%20topic%20is%20because%20I've%20been%20there%20so%20long.%20There%20are%20folks%20that%20I%20run%20into%20who%20I%20worked%20with%20on%20a%20project%20years%20ago%2C%20but%20maybe%20haven't%20seen%20since.%20So%20sometimes%20it's%20catching%20up%20work-wise%2C%20sometimes%20it's%20catching%20up%20socially.%20Sometimes%20it's%20about%20a%20new%20product%20idea.%20Sometimes%20it's%20about%20somebody%20wanting%20to%20pull%20me%20into%20a%20meeting.%20Recently%2C%20we%20had%20about%2020%20drivers%20at%20the%20office%20to%20do%20a%20driver%20roundtable%20with%20executives.%20I%20had%20first%20learned%20about%20that%20roundtable%20a%20week%20or%20two%20before%20by%20running%20into%20somebody%20who%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BHey%2C%20we're%20having%20drivers%20the%20office%2C%20like%20can%20you%20block%20this%20time%20on%20your%20calendar%3F%26quot%3B%20They're%20just%20all%20these%20little%20fortuitous%20moments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20is%20the%20number%201%20request%20from%20customers%3F%20From%20drivers%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Women%2B%20Connect%20was%20a%20major%20one%20that%20we%20had%20gotten%20so%20many%20times%20through%20the%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20things%20that%20bubbled%20up%20last%20week%20as%20a%20fairly%20consistent%20theme%20was%20customer%20service%2C%20that%20it's%20difficult%20to%20get%20through%20and%20it's%20difficult%20to%20get%20problems%20answered.%20And%20this%20was%20tough%20to%20hear%2C%20but%20in%20some%20ways%20heartening%2C%20because%20like%20I%20said%2C%20with%20our%20new%20customer%20obsessed%20orientation%2C%20it's%20actually%20something%20that%20we've%20already%20been%20really%2C%20really%20actively%20working%20on.%20And%20so%20that%20feedback%20was%20validating%20that%20we%20are%20on%20the%20right%20track%20to%20fixing%20some%20of%20the%20things%20that%20users%20need%20the%20most.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flyft-president-career-advice-women-in-workplace-taylor-swift-song-2023-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701089101000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65561cfa36d588dc55d15e56%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flyft-president-career-advice-women-in-workplace-taylor-swift-song-2023-11%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Lyft's%20Kristen%20Sverchek%20talks%20about%20taking%20leaps%20of%20faith%2C%20validating%20her%20decisions%2C%20and%20the%20Taylor%20Swift%20song%20she%20uses%20to%20pump%20up%20her%20team%2C%20and%20herself.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jrose%40insider.com%20(Jos%C3%A9e%20Rose)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flyft-president-career-advice-women-in-workplace-taylor-swift-song-2023-11%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Chris%20Evans'%20wife%20Alba%20flaunts%20wedding%20ring%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701089086000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-105537328%2Cimgsize-39512.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3