9.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Sri%20Lanka%20Sports%20Minister%20Sacked%20After%20Massive%20'Assassination'%20Claim%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ESri%20Lanka's%20sports%20minister%20Roshan%20Ranasinghe%C2%A0was%20sacked%20on%20Monday%20hours%20after%20he%20accused%20President%20Ranil%20Wickremesinghe%20of%20trying%20to%20assassinate%20him%20over%20his%20moves%20to%20clean%20up%20corruption%20at%20the%20cricket%20board.%20Officials%20said%20Roshan%20Ranasinghe%20was%20dismissed%20ahead%20of%20Monday's%20weekly%20cabinet%20meeting%20after%20he%20told%20parliament%20that%20Wickremesinghe%20should%20be%20held%20responsible%20if%20he%20was%20killed.%20%26quot%3BI%20fear%20I%20could%20be%20killed%20over%20my%20work%20to%20clean%20up%20the%20cricket%20board%2C%26quot%3B%20Ranasinghe%20told%20parliament%2C%20escalating%20a%20confrontation%20with%20Wickremesinghe%20who%20had%20been%20at%20loggerheads%20with%20the%20minister%20over%20the%20running%20of%20Sri%20Lanka%20Cricket.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20I%20am%20assassinated%20on%20the%20road%2C%20the%20president%20and%20his%20chief%20of%20staff%20will%20be%20responsible%2C%26quot%3B%20Ranasinghe%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20no%20immediate%20reaction%20from%20Wickremesinghe%20except%20confirmation%20from%20his%20office%20that%20the%20minister%20was%20dismissed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERanasinghe%20sacked%20the%20elected%20cricket%20board%20earlier%20this%20month%20after%20accusing%20office-bearers%20of%20gross%20corruption%2C%20a%20charge%20they%20have%20denied%20and%20are%20challenging%20in%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20cricket%20board%20is%20the%20richest%20sporting%20organisation%20in%20the%20otherwise%20bankrupt%20island%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20International%20Cricket%20Council%20suspended%20Sri%20Lanka%20Cricket%20(SLC)%20earlier%20this%20month%2C%20saying%20it%20had%20failed%20to%20ensure%20there%20was%20no%20government%20interfere