ied%20by%20their%20children%2C%20Viaan%20and%20Samisha.%20Shilpa%20Shetty%20extended%20warm%20wishes%20to%20her%20followers%20on%20Guru%20Nanak%20Jayanti%20through%20her%20Instagram%20stories%2C%20sharing%20a%20heartfelt%20message.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BBoys%20Are%20Taking%20Responsibility%26quot%3B%3A%20SKY's%20Massive%20Praise%20For%20India%20Teammates%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFollowing%20his%20side's%2044-run%20win%20over%20Australia%20in%20the%20second%20T20I%2C%20Indian%20skipper%20Suryakumar%20Yadav%20said%20that%20captaincy%20and%20team%20is%20not%20putting%20much%20pressure%20on%20me%2C%20but%20rather%20boys%20are%20taking%20responsibility%20well.%20In%20another%20domination-filled%20day%20for%20Men%20in%20Blue%2C%20India%2C%20led%20by%20three-wicket%20hauls%20from%20Prasidh%20Krishna%20and%20Ravi%20Bishnoi%20and%20fifties%20from%20Yashasvi%20Jaiswal%2C%20Ishan%20Kishan%20and%20Ruturaj%20Gaikwad%2C%20beat%20Australia%20by%2044%20runs%20in%20the%20second%20T20I%20of%20the%20five-match%20series%20at%20Thiruvananthapuram%20on%20Sunday.%20%26quot%3BThe%20boys%20aren't%20putting%20too%20much%20pressure%20on%20me%2C%20they're%20taking%20responsibility.%20I%20told%20them%20before%20the%20toss%20to%20be%20prepared%20to%20bat%20first.%20There%20was%20a%20lot%20of%20dew%20after%20three%20overs%2C%20told%20the%20boys%20to%20back%20themselves.%20When%20I%20saw%20Rinku%20in%20the%20last%20game%2C%20the%20composure%20was%20brilliant%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Suryakumar%20in%20a%20post-match%20presentation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20lead%20the%20series%202-0.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EComing%20to%20the%20match%2C%20Australia%20opted%20to%20field%20first.%20Half-centuries%20came%20from%20Yashasvi%20Jaiswal%20(53%20in%2025%20balls%2C%20with%20nine%20fours%20and%20two%20sixes)%20and%20Ruturaj%20Gaikwad%20(58%20in%2043%20balls%2C%20with%20three%20fours%20and%20two%20sixes).%20These%20openers%20put%20on%20a%20stand%20of%2077%20runs%20for%20the%20first%20wicket.%20Another%20half-century%20was%20scored%20by%20Ishan%20Kishan%2C%20who%20ended%20with%2052%20in%2032%20balls%2C%20with%20three%20fours%20and%20four%20sixes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENathan%20Ellis%20(3%2F45)%20and%20Marcus%20Stoinis%20(1%2F27)%20were%20among%20the%20wickets%20for%20Aussies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EComing%20to%20the%20chase%20of%20236%2C%20Australia%20was%20off%20to%20a%20terrible%20start%20and%20was%20reduced%20to%2058%2F4.%20An%2081-run%20stand%20between%20Marcus%20Stoinis%20(45%20in%2025%20balls%2C%20with%20two%20fours%20and%20four%20sixes)%20and%20Tim%20David%20(37%20in%2022%20balls%2C%20with%20four%20boundaries%20and%20two%20sixes)%20threatened%20India%20temporarily%2C%20but%20a%20fightback%20by%20Men%20in%20Blue%20saw%20them%20restrict%20Australia%20to%20191%2F9%20in%2020%20overs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERavi%20Bishnoi%20(3%2F32)%20and%20Prasidh%20Krishna%20(3%2F41)%20were%20the%20top%20bowlers%20for%20India.%20Axar%20Patel%2C%20Arshdeep%20Singh%20and%20Mukesh%20Kumar%20got%20one%20wicket%20each.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701083580000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2F6n6drrco_p_625x300_27_November_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Faustralia-tour-of-india-2023%2Findia-vs-australia-boys-are-taking-responsibility-suryakumar-yadavs-massive-praise-for-india-teammates-4608610%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Suryakumar%20Yadav%20said%20that%20captaincy%20and%20team%20is%20not%20putting%20much%20pressure%20on%20me%2C%20but%20rather%20boys%20are%20taking%20responsibility%20well.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Faustralia-tour-of-india-2023%2Findia-vs-australia-boys-are-taking-responsibility-suryakumar-yadavs-massive-praise-for-india-teammates-4608610%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.amp