p%3EThe%20move%20holds%20no%20surprises.%20That%20Pandian%20%E2%80%93%20a%20Tamil%20Nadu-born%20IAS%20officer%20originally%20alloted%20to%20the%20Punjab%20cadre%20who%20came%20to%20live%20and%20work%20in%20Odisha%20only%20after%20getting%20married%20to%20an%20Odia%20colleague%20%E2%80%93%20enjoys%20Patnaik%E2%80%99s%20trust%20has%20been%20well%20known.%20As%20the%20sole%20gatekeeper%20to%20the%20ageing%20and%20reticent%20Odisha%20patriarch%2C%20Pandian%20wielded%20enormous%20power%20both%20within%20and%20outside%20the%20party%20that%20has%20ruled%20the%20state%20without%20interruption%20since%202000.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGiven%20his%20unmatched%20influence%2C%20that%20Pandian%20is%20eyeing%20to%20be%20the%20successor%20to%20Patnaik%20as%20and%20when%20he%20exits%20the%20political%20stage%20has%20also%20had%20a%20ring%20of%20certainty.%20It%20was%20reinforced%20further%20when%20he%20quit%20the%20IAS%20a%20few%20weeks%20ago%20and%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fvk-pandian-step-closer-naveen-patnaik-successor%5C%22%3Epromptly%20made%20the%20chairperson%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20two%20state%20government%20initiatives%20with%20cabinet%20minister%20rank.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20induction%20into%20the%20party%20strengthens%20the%20popular%20perception%20that%20Pandian%20is%20in%20pole%20position%20to%20succeed%20Patnaik%2C%20a%20bachelor%20with%20no%20biological%20heirs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20Pandian%E2%80%99s%20joining%20the%20BJD%20possibly%20tells%20us%20is%20that%20the%20chief%20minister%20likes%20him%20more%20than%20anyone%20else%20and%20that%20the%20ex-bureaucrat%20in%20all%20likelihood%20is%20his%20choice%20as%20the%20successor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20while%20speculations%20over%20the%20succession%20can%20now%20be%20considered%20to%20be%20more%20or%20less%20settled%2C%20a%20bigger%20question%20still%20looms%3A%20Will%20Odias%2C%20who%20like%20the%20chief%20minister%2C%20like%20his%20choice%20as%20well%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20one%20has%20to%20wait%20longer%20to%20find%20out%20the%20answer%2C%20there%20is%20little%20to%20doubt%20any%20more%20that%20Patnaik%20is%20relying%20on%20the%20goodwill%20he%20enjoys%20to%20push%20through%20his%20choice.%20A%20non-Odia%20being%20pitchforked%20to%20be%20the%20future%20CM%20could%20be%20unimaginable%20in%20any%20other%20state.%20But%20Odisha%20has%20proven%20to%20be%20different%20in%20the%20past.%20Patnaik%20became%20the%20chief%20minister%20of%20Odisha%20when%20he%20spoke%20no%20Odia.%20Patnaik%2C%20by%20all%20accounts%2C%20is%20hoping%20that%20Odias%20will%20be%20as%20forgiving%20to%20the%20non-Odia%20Pandian.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPropelled%20by%20that%20conviction%2C%20Patnaik%20as%20well%20as%20his%20government%20and%20party%20have%20left%20no%20stone%20unturned%20to%20pave%20the%20way%20for%20Pandian%E2%80%99s%20prominence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20hindsight%2C%20the%20recent%20Odisha%20government%20move%20to%20gather%20public%20grievances%20by%20sending%20Pandian%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fodisha-ias-officer-karthikeyan-pandian-naveen-patnaik-successor%5C%22%3Ewhirlwind%20helicopter%20trips%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20all%20districts%20of%20the%20state%20was%20cleverly%20orchestrated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPandian%E2%80%99s%20public%20profile%20went%20up%20several%20notches%20as%20the%20state%20spent%20crores%20of%20public%20money%20to%20organise%20for%20him%20the%20elaborate%20rallies%20attended%20by%20thousands.%20The%20government%20and%20the%20chief%20minister%20insisted%20the%20spectacle%20rolled%20out%20over%20some%20six%20months%20was%20to%20bring%20the%20CMO%20(Chief%20Minister%E2%80%99s%20Office)%20to%20the%20doorstep%20of%20the%20common%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20a%20palpable%20lie.%20For%20one%2C%20Pandian%20as%20the%20private%20secretary%20to%20the%20chief%20minister%2C%20was%20only%20one%20among%20the%2015%20officers%20in%20the%20CMO.%20He%20was%20also%20not%20the%20senior%20most.%20But%20it%20was%20only%20him%20who%20one%20saw%20touring%20the%20state%20amid%20mega%20publicity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMore%20importantly%2C%20even%20the%20chief%20minister%E2%80%99s%20assertion%20in%20the%20assembly%20later%20that%20the%20move%20to%20send%20CMO%20officials%20was%20to%20lessen%20the%20financial%20burden%20of%20common%20people%20who%20otherwise%20would%20have%20been%20required%20to%20spend%20own%20money%20to%20visit%20government%20departments%20to%20lodge%20their%20complaints%2C%20did%20not%20wash.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20it%20turned%20out%2C%20the%20Odisha%20government%20spent%20more%20than%20what%20an%20ordinary%20Odia%20would%20have%20had%20to%20spend.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGoing%20by%20what%20Patnaik%20told%20the%20assembly%2C%20the%20government%20spent%20some%20Rs%201.5%20crore%20per%20month%20for%20six%20months%20to%20gather%20the%20grievances.%20It%20translated%20into%20Rs%209%20crores%20in%20total.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%2057%2C000%20grievances%20were%20collected%20during%20the%20six-month%20drive.%20The%20government%20expenditure%20to%20collect%20each%20grievance%20therefore%20worked%20out%20to%20Rs%201%2C578.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20a%20highly%20skilled%20Odia%20worker%20would%20have%20spent%20much%20less%20%E2%80%93%20just%20Rs%201%2C004%20%E2%80%93%20if%20he%20or%20she%20had%20to%20go%20to%20the%20district%20collector%20to%20complain%2C%20spending%20some%20two%20days%2C%20since%20the%20daily%20wage%20for%20such%20workers%20is%20Rs%20502%20only.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20money%20spent%20would%20have%20been%20far%20less%20for%20unskilled%20or%20moderately%20skilled%20workers%2C%20their%20daily%20wages%20being%20much%20lower.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20plain%20mathematics%20simply%20did%20not%20matter%20for%20Patnaik%2C%20hell-bent%20on%20promoting%20Pandian.%20The%20high-profile%20tours%20over%2C%20Pandian%20quit%20the%20IAS%2C%20taking%20up%20a%20more%20public%20role%20as%20chairperson%20of%20state%20government%20initiatives%20with%20cabinet%20minister