%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Fms-dhoni-sings-channa-mereya-with-taylor-swift-ai-generated-song-is-viral-4609966%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Beyond%20Lord%20Ram%2C%20Lord%20Kubera's%20Blessings%20Crucial%20For%202024%20Polls%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Sangh%20Parivar's%20mandate%20for%20Lord%20Ram%20in%20the%201980s%20was%20to%20bring%20the%20BJP%20power.%20While%20the%20mighty-armed%20prince%20of%20the%20epic%20Ramayana%20played%20his%20part%20in%20the%20BJP%20getting%20its%20first%20taste%20of%20power%20at%20the%20Centre%20in%201996%20and%20a%20relatively%20smaller%20role%20in%20delivering%20the%20country%20in%202014%2C%20it%20was%20Narendra%20Modi's%20promise%20of%20a%20glittering%20future%20that%20really%20made%20the%20difference.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20lord%20is%20still%20being%20put%20to%20work%20for%20the%20party%20trying%20to%20eke%20out%20the%20temple%20movement's%20dividends.%20For%20instance%2C%20Home%20Minister%20and%20BJP%20leader%20Amit%20Shah%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FBJP4India%2Fstatus%2F1724724971979813328%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%3Ebeseeched%3C%2Fa%3E%20Chhattisgarh%20voters%20saying%20the%20state%20was%20Lord%20Ram's%20maternal%20grandparents'%20home.%20Shah%20said%20%26quot%3Btheir%20nephew%26quot%3B%20was%20about%20to%20be%20seated%20in%20his%20new%20abode%20in%20Ayodhya%20because%20of%20Modi%20who%20laid%20its%20foundation%20stone%20and%20will%20consecrate%20the%20completed%20structure%20in%20the%20New%20Year.%20He%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Felections%2Fassembly-elections%2Ftelangana-assembly-elections%2Fvote-for-bjp-we-would-arrange-free-darshan-of-ram-temple-in-ayodhya-for-all-amit-shah-in-telangana%2Farticleshow%2F105312221.cms%5C%22%3Epromised%3C%2Fa%3E%20free%20visits%20to%20Ayodhya%20for%20all%20residents%20of%20Telangana%20if%20they%20chose%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20nearly%20a%20decade%20after%20the%20BJP%20captured%20Delhi%20with%20a%20resounding%20majority%2C%20the%20marginal%20utility%20of%20Ram%2C%20the%20first%20unifier%20of%20the%20Hindu%20nation%20per%20the%20originator%20of%20the%20Hindutva%20ideology%2C%20VD%20Savarkar%2C%20is%20minimal.%20If%20there%20is%20one%20deity%20that%20needs%20propitiating%20for%20the%20future%2C%20that%20is%20Ravana's%20half-brother%20Kubera%2C%20the%20lord%20of%20wealth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20any%20dispensation%20that%20comes%20to%20power%20will%20have%20to%20hope%20for%20Kubera's%20beneficence%20to%20lift%20millions%20of%20Indians%20out%20of%20misery%2C%20provide%20jobs%20to%20young%20aspirants%2C%20and%20protect%20its%20borders%2C%20land%20and%20water%20from%20enemy%20and%20nature.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20all%20the%20positive%20vibes%20from%20foreign%20investors%2C%20and%20pep%20talk%20from%20Indian%20industrialists%2C%20the%20economy%20is%20precariously%20poised.%20Most%20estimates%20suggest%20output%20will%20grow%20at%20a%20rate%20between%206%25%20and%207%25%20this%20year%20and%20the%20next.%20Public%20finances%20are%20not%20in%20the%20shape%20any%20government%20would%20like%20them%20to%20be.%20The%20cost%20of%20highway%20construction%2C%20the%20most%20visually%20appealing%20advertisement%20for%20development%2C%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.financialexpress.com%2Fbusiness%2Froadways-bharatmala-pariyojana-project-cost-soars-to-rs-10-64-lakh-crore-more-than-doubles-reports-icra-3312399%2F%5C%22%3Edoubled%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20more%20than%20Rs%2010.64%20lakh%20crore.%20The%20cabinet%20has%20hesitated%20to%20clear%20the%20steep%20cost%20overrun%20which%20has%20resulted%20in%20project%20awards%20falling%20by%2048%25%20in%20the%20first%20half%20of%20the%20current%20fiscal%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20has%20temporarily%20kept%20prices%20under%20control%20by%20restricting%20exports%20of%20key%20staples%20such%20as%20wheat%2C%20rice%20and%20sugar%2C%20hoping%20fresh%20harvest%20would%20ease%20the%20burden.%20But%20erratic%20weather%20is%20likely%20to%20play%20havoc%20again.%20Crop%20acreage%20in%20Maharashtra%20is%20likely%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdaily.thesignal.co%2Fp%2Fopen-ai-sam-altman-nvidia-inflation%23%C2%A7maha-prices%5C%22%3Esuffer%3C%2Fa%3E%20due%20to%20water%20shortage.%20Reports%20suggest%20that%20reservoirs%20have%2020%25%20less%20storage%20than%20at%20the%20same%20time%20the%20previous%20year.%20Floods%2C%20storms%2C%20droughts%20etc.%20are%20estimated%20to%20have%20wiped%20out%20crops%20on%2036%20million%20hectares%20in%20the%20state%20in%20the%20past%20five%20years.%20Maharashtra%20is%20a%20critical%20supplier%20of%20kitchen%20staples%20such%20as%20onions%2C%20sugar%2C%20and%20pulses.%20It's%20also%20a%20major%20producer%20of%20grapes%20and%20mangoes%2C%20both%20key%20export%20commodities.%20Crop%20shrinkage%20could%20lead%20to%20higher%20prices%20next%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFood%20inflation%20has%20been%20a%20regular%20disrupter%20of%20household%20budgets%20in%20the%20past%20couple%20of%20years.%20Add%20to%20that%20external%20factors%20such%20as%20oil%20prices.%20An%20uptick%20in%20the%20global%20economy%20will%20push%20up%20energy%20prices.%20Wall%20Street%20biggie%20Goldman%20Sachs%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fbusiness%2Ffinance%2Findia-cenbank-could-raise-rates-if-oil-prices-see-sustained-rise-morgan-stanley-2023-11-06%2F%5C%22%3Eestimates%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20a%20%2410%20increase%20in%20oil%20prices%20pushes%20up%20India's%20inflation%20by%20half%20a%20percentage%20point%20and%20trade%20deficit%20by%200.3%20percentage%20points.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPersistent%20inflation%20will%20force%20the%20Reserve%20Bank%20of%20India%20to%20raise%20interest%20rates%2C%20which%20will%20increase%20overall%20costs%20in%20the%20economy.%20The%20central%20bank%20is%20already%20worried%20about%20household%20finances.%20It%20recently%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fbusiness%2Fbanking-and-finance%2Frbi-tightening-bankers-blame-high-nbfc-exposure-to-small-unsecured-loans-9040011%2F%5C%22%3Etightened%3C%2Fa%3E%20lending%20norms%20to%20make%20it%20tougher%20for%20banks%20and%20non-banking%20finance%20companies%20to%20dole%20out%20unsecured%20loans%20after%20consumers%20began%20borrowing%20heavily%20to%20buy%20gadgets%20and%20spend%20on%20holidays.%20Net%20household%20savings%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbctv18.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fhousehold-savings-hit-multi-decadal-lows-financial-liabilities-rise-assets-drop-17840861.htm%5C%22%3Edropped%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20nearly%20a%2050-year%20low.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20add%20to%20the%20stack%2C%20unemployment%20is%20rising%20alarmingly.%20Research%20firm%20Centre%20for%20Monitoring%20Indian%20Economy%20said%20joblessness%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Feconomy%2Findicators%2Findia-jobless-rate-rises-to-more-than-two-year-high-cmie-says%2Farticleshow%2F104893462.cms%5C%22%3Etopped%3C%2Fa%3E%2010%25%20in%20October%20reaching%20a%20two-year%20high%20as%20more%20people%20in%20rural%20areas%20could%20not%20find%20jobs.%20What's%20worrying%20is%20even%20sectors%20such%20as%20software%20services%20are%20facing%20the%20squeeze.%20For%20the%20first%20time%20in%20over%2025%20years%2C%20nine%20out%20of%20India's%20top%2010%20IT%20companies'%20workforces%20shrank%20in%20the%20first%20half%20of%20this%20fiscal%20year.%20That%20could%20mean%20we%20are%20past%20peak%20IT%20hiring.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20shortage%20of%20jobs%20and%20livelihoods%20has%20meant%20the%20government%20has%20had%20to%20scale%20up%20welfare%20measures%2C%20including%20food%20support.%20It%20is%20also%20said%20to%20be%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2023-10-11%2Fmodi-weighs-giving-small-farmers-more-cash-before-india-vote%5C%22%3Econsidering%3C%2Fa%3E%20increasing%20its%20dole%20for%20marginal%20farmers%20from%20Rs%206%2C000%20to%20Rs%208%2C000%20annually.%20The%20government%20was%20also%20forced%20to%20chew%20over%20restoring%20the%20employees'%20old%20pension%20scheme%2C%20which%20imposes%20substantial%20financial%20burden%20on%20its%20balance%20sheet%2C%20after%20it%20delivered%20electoral%20dividends%20to%20the%20opposition%20in%20state%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20global%20headwinds%20will%20continue%20to%20buffet%20the%20economy%2C%20the%20impulse%20for%20unrestrained%2C%20competitive%20populism%20would%20be%20a%20disaster.%20But%20it%20might%20be%20futile%20to%20hope%20for%20moderation%20as%20opposition%20parties%20make%20a%20concerted%20bid%20to%20unseat%20Narendra%20Modi%20while%20the%20BJP%20pulls%20out%20every%20trick%20in%20its%20book%20to%20hang%20on%20to%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(The%20writer%20is%20editor%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdaily.thesignal.co%5C%22%3EThe%20Signal%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20author%20of%20The%20RSS%20And%20The%20Making%20Of%20The%20Deep%20Nation.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701079440000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Fcfvlbor_lord-ram-elections-afp_625x300_27_November_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fbeyond-lord-ram-lord-kuberas-blessings-crucial-for-2024-polls-4609788%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Sangh%20Parivar's%20mandate%20for%20Lord%20Ram%20in%20the%201980s%20was%20to%20bring%20the%20BJP%20power.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fbeyond-lord-ram-lord-kuberas-blessings-crucial-for-2024-polls-4609788%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fbeyond-lord-ram-lord-kuberas-blessings-crucial-for-2024-polls-4609788%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.c