ngi-re%2Farticleshow%2F105531457.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BIrreparable%20Loss%20For%20Farmers%26quot%3B%3A%20BRS%20On%20Poll%20Body%20Order%20Pausing%20Aid%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EHours%20after%20the%20Election%20Commission%20withdrew%20the%20permission%20it%20had%20given%20to%20the%20Telangana%20government%20to%20continue%20disbursing%20funds%20under%20a%20farmer%20assistance%20scheme%20during%20the%20model%20code%20of%20conduct%2C%20the%20Bharat%20Rashtra%20Samithi%20has%20said%20that%20doing%20so%20will%20cause%20irreparable%20loss%20to%20the%20farmers%20and%20requested%20the%20panel%20to%20reconsider%20its%20decision.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20reason%20given%20by%20the%20Election%20Commission%20for%20pausing%20the%20financial%20aid%20to%20farmers%20under%20the%20Rythu%20Bandhu%20scheme%20was%20that%20a%20state%20minister%20had%20violated%20the%20conditions%20for%20the%20permission%20by%20making%20a%20public%20announcement%20about%20the%20release%20of%20funds%20under%20the%20scheme%20while%20the%20model%20code%20of%20conduct%20was%20in%20force.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20letter%20to%20the%20Election%20Commission%2C%20the%20ruling%20party%20has%20said%20that%20the%20minister%20was%20not%20promoting%20the%20scheme%20but%20only%20thanking%20the%20panel%20for%20allowing%20it%20to%20continue%20with%20the%20disbursement.%20It%20also%20pointed%20out%20that%20the%20disbursal%20of%20funds%20under%20a%20Central%20scheme%20is%20still%20happening.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20order%20issued%20on%20Monday%2C%20the%20Election%20Commission%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20Commission%20has%20observed%20that%20T%20Harish%20Rao%2C%20Minister%20of%20Finance%20and%20Heath%20and%20Family%20Welfare%2C%20Govt%20of%20Telangana%20...%20has%20not%20only%20violated%20the%20provisions%20of%20MCC%20(model%20code%20of%20conduct)...%20but%20also%20conditions%20laid%20down%20as%20above%20by%20publicising%20the%20release%20under%20the%20scheme%2C%20and%20thereby%20disturbed%20the%20level%20playing%20field%20in%20the%20ongoing%20election%20process.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Commission%20has%20directed%20that%20the%20permission%20granted%20vide%20its%20letter%20dated%20November%2025%2C%202023%2C%20for%20disbursement%20of%20rabi%20season%20instalment%20under%20the%20ongoing%20Rythu%20Bandhu%20scheme%20during%20currency%20of%20MCC%2C%20shall%20stand%20withdrawn%20immediately%20and%20there%20shall%20be%20no%20disbursement%20under%20the%20Scheme%20till%20the%20Model%20Code%20of%20Conduct%20in%20the%20State%20of%20Telangana%20ceases%20to%20apply%20in%20all%20its%20forms%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20commission%20said%20in%20a%20letter%20to%20the%20Telangana%20chief%20electoral%20officer.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVoting%20for%20the%20Telangana%20Assembly%20election%20will%20take%20place%20on%20Thursday%20and%20the%20model%20code%20will%20stay%20in%20force%20till%20December%203%2C%20when%20the%20counting%20will%20happen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20letter%20to%20the%20poll%20body%2C%20the%20BRS%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20submitted%20that%20Shri%20T.%20Harish%20Rao%20has%20not%20made%20any%20such%20comment%20which%20is%20in%20violation%20of%20your%20order%20dated%2025.11.2023.%20He%20merely%20thanked%20your%20authority%20for%20allowing%20the%20disbursement%20of%20scheme%20amount%20to%20the%20farmers%20in%20the%20state%20of%20Telangana.%20This%20statement%20of%20Shri%20T%20Harish%20Rao%20is%20an%20inadvertent%20statement%20and%20nothing%20but%20an%20expression%20of%20gratitude%20for%20the%20Election%20Commission's%20decision.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20pointed%20out%20that%20farmers%20have%20begun%20cultivation%20for%20the%20rabi%20season%20and%20the%20Rythu%20Bandhu%20scheme%20has%20been%20on%20since%20the%20past%20five-and-a-half%20years.%20The%20party%20said%20that%20disbursal%20is%20being%20allowed%20under%20the%20Union%20government's%20PM%20Kisan%20scheme%20and%20%26quot%3Bthere%20is%20no%20difference%20between%20both%20the%20schemes%20so%20far%20as%20assistance%20to%20the%20farmers%20is%20considered%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20stoppage%20of%20disbursement%20would%20cause%20irreparable%20loss%20to%20the%20farmers%20since%20the%20agricultural%20season%20would%20be%20lost.%20Therefore%2C%20we%20request%20you%20to%20take%20a%20right%20view%20and%20withdraw%20the%20order%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20letter%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701077460000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2020-04%2F1kpjqlto_farming-generic-650_625x300_07_April_20.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Felection-commission-rythu-bandhu-irreparable-loss-for-farmers-brs-on-poll-body-order-pausing-aid-4609735%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Hours%20after%20the%20Election%20Commission%20withdrew%20the%20permission%20it%20had%20given%20to%20the%20Telangana%20government%20to%20continue%20disbursing%20funds%20under%20a%20farmer%20assistance%20scheme%2C%20the%20Bharat%20Rashtra%20Samithi%20has%20said%20doing%20so%20will%20cause%20%26quot%3Birreparable%20loss%26quot%3B%20to%20farmers.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Felection-commission-rythu-bandhu-irreparable-loss-for-farmers-brs-on-poll-body-order-pausing-aid-4609735%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Felection-commission-rythu-bandhu-irreparable-loss-for-farmers-brs-on-poll-body-order-pausing-aid-4609735%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Felection-commission-rythu-bandhu-irreparable-loss-for-farmers-brs-on-poll-body-order-pausing-aid-4609735%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Class%204%20Boys%20Attack%20Classmate%20With%20Compass%20108%20Times%20After%20Fight%20At%20School%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20student%20of%20Class%204%20was%20alle