as%20meant%20to%20be%20carried%20alongside%20Wagh%E2%80%99s%20poem%20%E2%80%98Secular%E2%80%99%2C%20but%20the%20text%20was%20removed%20on%20Saturday%20(November%2025).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20poem%20is%20republished%20at%20the%20end%20of%20this%20article.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20newspaper%2C%20Wagh%E2%80%99s%20nephew%2C%20Kaustubh%20Naik%2C%20called%20it%20an%20%E2%80%9Cact%20of%20censorship%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENaik%20told%20the%20daily%20that%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Peacock%3C%2Fem%3E%20team%20had%20asked%20him%20a%20few%20days%20ago%20to%20translate%20the%20poem%20from%20Wagh%E2%80%99s%20collection%20titled%20%E2%80%98Sudirsukta%E2%80%99.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20wanted%20me%20to%20vet%20some%20poems.%20I%20asked%20them%20if%20they%20had%20any%20specific%20poem%20in%20mind%20and%20was%20asked%20to%20translate%20this%20particular%20one.%20The%20poem%20was%20to%20accompany%20a%20double-page%20spread%20illustration%20on%20Wagh%20by%20the%20anti-caste%20artist%20Siddhesh%20Gautam%20in%20the%20Sunday%20edition%20of%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Peacock%3C%2Fem%3E.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20on%20Saturday%2C%20the%20Entertainment%20Society%20of%20Goa%20(ESG)%20officials%20informed%20him%20that%20the%20poem%20would%20not%20be%20included%20in%20the%20print.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20the%20poem%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9Canti-establishment%20stance%E2%80%9D%20and%20themes%20could%20be%20one%20of%20the%20reasons%20to%20not%20print%20the%20poem.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20poetry%20collection%20Sudirsukta%20caused%20some%20controversy%20in%202017%20%E2%80%A6%20If%20you%20read%20the%20collection%2C%20you%20realise%20that%20Wagh%20recorded%20histories%20of%20Goa%E2%80%99s%20Bahujan%20Samaj%20through%20his%20poems.%20The%20use%20of%20language%20and%20its%20imagery%20and%20themes%20are%20rather%20revolutionary%20in%20Goa%E2%80%99s%20literary%20scene.%20The%20poems%20take%20an%20anti-establishment%20stance.%20Perhaps%20that%E2%80%99s%20the%20reason%2C%E2%80%9D%20Naik%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20unfortunate%20that%20this%20act%20of%20censorship%20occurred%20on%20the%20eve%20of%20Constitution%20day%20%5BNovember%2025%5D%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202017%2C%20Wagh%E2%80%99s%20anthology%20of%20poems%20in%20Konkani%2C%20titled%20%E2%80%98Sudirsukta%20%E2%80%93%20Hymns%20of%20a%20Shudra%2C%E2%80%99%20got%20the%20Goa%20Konkani%20Academy%20Award%20in%20the%20poetry%20category.%20However%2C%20controversy%20ensued%20when%20news%20of%20the%20award%20%E2%80%9Cleaked%20before%20the%20official%20announcement%2C%E2%80%9D%20leading%20to%20allegations%20that%20the%20book%20endorsed%20communal%20views.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbooks%2Fgoa-poet-first-awarded-hounded-police-questioning-brahmins%5C%22%3Ewas%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20a%20social%20media%20campaign%20lifted%20its%20verses%20and%20shared%20them%20%E2%80%9Cout%20of%20context%E2%80%9D%2C%20triggering%20a%20caste%20divide%20between%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20dominant%20Gaud%20Saraswat%20Brahmins%20(GSB)%20and%20the%20majority%20Bahujan%20Goans.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESubsequently%2C%20the%20awards%20for%20that%20year%20were%20cancelled%20by%20the%20then-chief%20minister%2C%20the%20late%20Manohar%20Parrikar%2C%20who%20incidentally%20belonged%20to%20the%20GSB%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGautam%20also%20expressed%20his%20disappointment%2C%20saying%2C%20on%20Instagram%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20asked%20to%20not%20publish%20a%20poem%20by%20Vishnu%20Surya%20Wagh%20for%20today%E2%80%99s%20issue.%20Wagh%E2%80%99s%20poem%20%E2%80%98Secular%E2%80%99%20(is%20one%20that)%20I%20carefully%20chose%20because%20it%20expresses%20so%20many%20incidents%20of%20caste%20discrimination%20by%20many%20on%20a%20daily%20basis%20in%20both%20urban%20and%20rural%20areas.%20I%20myself%20have%20gone%20through%20something%20similar%20many%20times%20in%20my%20life%2C%20not%20just%20as%20an%20unknown%20student%2C%20but%20also%20as%20a%20well-known%20artist.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ESG%20is%20the%20nodal%20agency%20that%20organises%20IFFI%20on%20behalf%20of%20the%20Goa%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20told%20the%20newspaper%20that%20the%20decision%20not%20to%20include%20the%20poem%20was%20taken%20%E2%80%9Cpurely%20for%20creative%20reasons%E2%80%9D.%20ESG%20is%20also%20the%20publisher%20of%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Peacock%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EESG%20CEO%20Ankita%20Mishra%20told%20the%20daily%20that%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20decision%20to%20not%20print%20the%20article%20was%20an%20editorial%20call%20taken%20purely%20for%20creative%20reasons%20and%20had%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20the%20content%20of%20the%20article.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C(The)%20%3Cem%3EPeacock%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20been%20a%20flagbearer%20for%20artistic%20freedom%20since%20its%20inception%2C%20and%20it%20is%20our%20endeavour%20that%20it%20continues%20to%20be%20so%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FC0GOnRQSNkl%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26ig_rid%3D9e9cfe10-95c1-4bcb-b45d-17efd77f0c4c%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESecular%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(By%20Vishnu%20Surya%20Wagh%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ETranslated%20by%20Kaustubh%20Naik)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EI%20was%20unaware%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cem%3EOf%20their%20technique%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cem%3ETo%20sniff%20people%E2%80%99s%20caste%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EOne%20day%2C%20visiting%20a%20friend%E2%80%99s%20house%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cem%3EEncountered%20his%20uncle%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cem%3ELounging%20on%20the%20balc%C3%A3o%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cem%3EAnd%20we%20began%20conversing%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CWagh%3F%20You%E2%80%99re%20one%20of%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cem%3EUncle%20smirked.%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cem%3EI%20felt%20a%20pang%20of%20anxiety.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EYet%2C%20he%20sought%20absolute%20certainty.%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cem%3ESo%20he%20inquired%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Kamat%20Waghs%20of%20Ribandar%2C%20kin%20to%20you%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CNo%2C%E2%80%9D%20I%20replied.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CHailing%20from%20Karwar%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CNo%2C%20I%E2%80%99m%20from%20Goa.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CIndeed%3F%20Which%20part%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CFrom%20Dongri%3F%20Perhaps%20the%20Mahajans%20of%20the%20Rama%20temple%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CNo.%20Our%20goddess%20is%20Sati.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EStill%20unable%20to%20deduce%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cem%3EHe%20probed%20once%20more.%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CWho%20is%20your%20family%20deity%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CShivnath%2C%E2%80%9D%20I%20offered.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CFrom%20Shiroda%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CYes.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CSo%E2%80%A6so%20you%20are%20not%20a%20GSB.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CNo%2C%20uncle%2C%20we%20are%20Bhandaris.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EA%20chuckle%20escaped%20him.%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CDon%E2%80%99t%20take%20offense!%20I%20asked%20out%20of%20curiosity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cem%3EWe%20renounce%20caste.%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cem%3ECome%2C%20have%20tea.%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cem%3ECaste%20systems%20have%20marred%20Goa.%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cem%3EWho%20is%20Baman%3F%20Who%20is%20Shudra%3F%20Who%20cares%3F%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cem%3EThese%20divisions%20hold%20no%20meaning.%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cem%3EWe%20should%20be%20secular.%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cem%3EWe%20must%20have%20a%20casteless%20society%2C%20you%20know%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EUncle%20waited%2C%20anticipation%20in%20the%20air%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EI%20merely%20nodded%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ESipping%20tea%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EMy%20gaze%2C%20firm%20on%20his%20sacred%20thread%E2%80%99s%20descent%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701071731000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F10%2Fvishnu.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fiffl-dailys-refusal-to-print-konkani-poem-on-caste-discrimination-draws-criticism%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Sunday%20edition%20of%20the%20daily%2C%20'The%20Peacock'%2C%20was%20meant%20to%20carry%20late%20Goan%20writer%20and%20former%20BJP%20MLA%20Vishnu%20Surya%20Wagh's%20poem%20'Secular'%2C%20but%20the%20text%20was%20removed%20on%20Saturday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A7%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fiffl-dailys-refusal-to-print-konkani-poem-on-caste-discrimination-draws-criticism%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Three%20students%20of%20Palestinian%20descent%20shot%20in%20Vermont%2C%20suspect%20held%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701071434000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-105529898%2Cimgsize-1127553.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fthree-students-of-palestinian-descent-shot-in-vermont-suspect-held%2Farticleshow%2F105529780.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F105529780.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EA%20suspect%2C%20Jason%20J%20Eaton%2C%20was%20arrested%20in%20the%20shooting%20of%20three%20college%20students%20of%20Palestinian%20descent%20in%20Burlington%2C%20Vermont.%20The%20victims%20were%20identified%20as%20Hisham%20Awartani%2C%20Kinnan%20Abdel%20Hamid%2C%20and%20Tahseen%20Ahmed%2C%20who%20are%20graduates%20of%20the%20Ramallah%20Friends%20School.%20The%20attack%20is%20being%20investigated%20as%20a%20suspected%20hate%20crime%20and%20has%20prompted%20calls%20from%20the%20victims'%20families%2C%20the%20American-Arab%20Anti-Discrimination%20Committee%2C%20and%20the%20Institute%20for%20Middle%20East%20Understanding%20for%20a%20thorough%20investigation.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fthree-students-of-palestinian-descent-shot-in-vermont-suspect-held%2Farticleshow%2F105529780.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm-timesofindia-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fthree-students-of-palestinian-descent-shot-in-vermont-suspect-held%2Famp_articleshow%2F105529780.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fthree-students-of-palestinian-descent-shot-in-vermont-suspect-held%2Famp_articleshow%2F105529780.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20Weight%20of%20the%20World%20and%20Vikram%20Harijan's%20Shoulders%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F27131120%2FIMG-20231122-WA0134.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%E2%80%9CIf%20Lord%20Ram%20was%20alive%20today%2C%20I%20would%20have%20sent%20him%20to%20jail%20under%20section%20302%20of%20the%20IPC%20for%20the%20murder%20of%20Rishi%20Shambuk.%20And%20if%20Lord%20Krishna%20lived%20today%2C%20I%20would%20have%20sent%20him%20to%20jail%20under%20a%20case%20for%20sexual%20harassment%20of%20women.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20month%2C%20when%20Vikram%20Harijan%2C%20an%20assistant%20professor%20who%20teaches%20ancient%20and%20medieval%20history%20at%20the%20Allahabad%20University%2C%20posted%20this%20provocatively-worded%20tweet%20on%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter)%2C%20it%20triggered%20a%20barrage%20of%20outrage%20against%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHarijan%20belongs%20to%20a%20Dalit%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESection%20302%20of%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%20deals%20with%20murder.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20October%2022%2C%20Prayagraj%20police%20lodged%20an%20FIR%20against%20him%20for%20the%20tweet%2C%20accusing%20him%20of%20regularly%20insulting%20Hindu%20deities%20through%20%E2%80%9Cindecent%20and%20hateful%20comments.%E2%80%9D%20The%20police%20acted%20on%20a%20complaint%20by%20some%20right-wing%20groups%2C%20including%20the%20Bajrang%20Dal%2C%20and%20booked%20Harijan%20under%20Sections%20153A%20(promoting%20enmity%20between%20groups)%20and%20295A%20(deliberate%20and%20malicious%20act%20to%20outrage%20religious%20feelings)%20of%20the%20IPC%20and%20Section%2066%20of%20the%20Information%20Technology%20Act.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEvery%20other%20day%2C%20Harijan%20insults%20Hindu%20deities%20and%20this%20has%20created%20anger%20among%20students%20and%20also%20hurt%20the%20Hindu%20society%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Shubham%2C%20a%20Bajrang%20Dal%20activist%2C%20in%20the%20FIR.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHarijan%20approached%20the%20Allahabad%20high%20court%20pleading%20that%20the%20FIR%20against%20him%20be%20quashed.%20During%20the%20hearing%20of%20the%20petition%2C%20however%2C%20he%20sought%20protection%20under%20Section%2041-A%20of%20the%20CrPC%2C%20which%20stipulates%20that%20a%20person%20must%20be%20served%20notice%20by%20the%20police%20prior%20to%20his%20or%20her%20arrest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20November%208%2C%20a%20division%20bench%20of%20Justices%20Ashwani%20Kumar%20Mishra%20and%20Syed%20Aftab%20Husain%20Rizvi%20ruled%20that%20since%20the%20FIR%20prima%20facie%20disclosed%20commissioning%20of%20cognisable%20offence%2C%20it%20could%20not%20be%20quashed.%20However%2C%20the%20court%20directed%20the%20state%20authorities%20to%20ensure%20compliance%20of%20Section%2041-A%20of%20CrPC%20if%20its%20provisions%20were%20attracted%20in%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Harijan%20received%20legal%20relief%20against%20arbitrary%20arrest%2C%20his%20troubles%20did%20not%20end%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EUniversity%20serves%20notice%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Tuesday%2C%20November%2021%2C%20the%20university%20served%20him%20a%20show%20cause%20notice%20to%20submit%20his%20explanation%20for%20%E2%80%9Cposting%20outrageous%20comments%20against%20Hindu%20deities%20and%20culture%E2%80%9D%20on%20social%20media%20platforms%20within%20seven%20working%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20only%20the%20latest%20controversy%20that%20the%20outspoken%20Dalit%20professor%2C%20knowing%20for%20unabashedly%20voicing%20his%20critique%20of%20the%20caste%20system%20and%20dogmas%20of%20Hindu%20religion%2C%20has%20found%20himself%20in%20the%20last%20four%20years.%20He%20has%20invited%20the%20wrath%20of%20both%20right-wing%20groups%20as%20well%20as%20the%20university%20administration%20through%20his%20blunt%20articulation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%202019%2C%20the%20central%20varsity%20has%20served%20him%20notice%20and%20right-wing%20groups%20have%20registered%20complaints%20against%20him%20for%20targeting%20the%20Hindu%20faith%20on%20at%20least%20two%20other%20occasions.%20For%20the%20university%20and%20his%20critics%2C%20he%20is%20a%20provocateur.%20But%20for%20Harijan%2C%20he%20is%20expressing%20his%20freedom%20to%20rationally%20critique%20social%20practices%20and%20ideas%20linked%20to%20caste%2C%20a%20subject%20he%20feels%20strongly%20about.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Harijan%20said%20he%20used%20the%20references%20to%20the%20Hindu%20deities%20in%20his%20quest%20to%20%E2%80%9Cdevelop%20rationality%E2%80%9D%20among%20students%20and%20demonstrate%20to%20them%20the%20difference%20between%20modern%20democracy%20and%20autocratic%20states%20in%20ancient%2C%20medieval%20and%20modern%20periods.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDemocracy%20means%20a%20constitutional%20life%20based%20on%20rule%20of%20law.%20In%20that%20context%2C%20I%20stated%20this%20example%20that%20had%20these%20deities%20committed%20these%20acts%20in%20these%20times%2C%20what%20would%20have%20been%20the%20response%20to%20them.%20It%20was%20an%20emotional%20step%20towards%20teaching%20rationality%20to%20students%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20363px)%2085vw%2C%20363px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F27131639%2FScreenshot-2023-11-27-at-1.16.26%25E2%2580%25AFPM.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22363%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F27131639%2FScreenshot-2023-11-27-at-1.16.26%25E2%2580%25AFPM.png%20660w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F27131639%2FScreenshot-2023-11-27-at-1.16.26%25E2%2580%25AFPM-205x300.png%20205w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-686529%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22530%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EVikram%20Harijan.%20Photo%3A%20By%20arrangement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EShambuk%20and%20the%20rage%20of%20the%20years%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENot%20restricted%20to%20academic%20expression%2C%20the%20motivation%20to%20use%20these%20references%20also%20stems%20from%20his%20%E2%80%9Cinternal%20rage%E2%80%9D%20on%20the%20issue%20of%20caste%20discrimination%20and%20his%20lived%20experiences%20as%20a%20Dalit.%20The%20story%20of%20Shambuk%2C%20a%20reference%20to%20which%20has%20landed%20him%20in%20a%20soup%2C%20has%20often%20been%20used%20by%20scholars%20to%20illustrate%20caste%20hierarchy%20and%20discrimination%20in%20the%20Ramayana.%20B.R.%20Ambedkar%20refers%20to%20it%20in%20his%20seminal%20work%20%3Cem%3EAnnihilation%20of%20Caste%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20also%20details%20it%20in%20the%20%3Cem%3ERiddles%20of%20Hinduism%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20which%20was%20posthumously%20published.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20story%20goes%20that%20when%20Ram%20was%20ruling%20Ayodhya%20as%20a%20king%2C%20a%20Brahmin%20man%20comes%20to%20him%2C%20weeping%2C%20with%20his%20dead%20son%20in%20his%20arms.%20The%20Brahmin%20concludes%20that%20his%20son%20died%20because%20the%20king%20may%20have%20committed%20a%20sin.%20A%20sage%20informs%20Ram%20that%20the%20Brahmin%E2%80%99s%20son%20died%20because%20a%20Shudra%20man%20in%20the%20kingdom%20was%20practising%20penance%2C%20in%20violation%20of%20the%20dharma.%20Ram%20goes%20to%20the%20said%20Shudra%20ascetic%2C%20Shambuk%2C%20who%20informs%20the%20king%20that%20he%20was%20performing%20penance%20to%20find%20a%20place%20in%20heaven.%20Rama%20punishes%20the%20Shudra%20for%20his%20transgression%20by%20cutting%20off%20his%20head.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmbedkar%20writes%20that%20to%20blame%20Ram%20for%20wantonly%20killing%20Shambuk%20was%20to%20misunderstand%20the%20situation.%20As%20a%20king%2C%20Ram%20was%20bound%20to%20maintain%20the%20Chaturvarna%20(four-tier%20caste%20system%20with%20low%20caste%20Shudras%20at%20the%20bottom)%2C%20which%20was%20the%20basis%20of%20Ram%20Raj%2C%20said%20Ambedkar.%20Therefore%2C%20it%20was%20his%20duty%20to%20kill%20Shambuk%20for%20transgressing%20his%20class%20and%20wanting%20to%20be%20a%20Brahmin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDravidian%20movement%20social%20reformer%20E.%20V.%20Ramasamy%20%E2%80%9CPeriyar%E2%80%9D%20had%20also%20expressed%20outrage%20over%20Ram%E2%80%99s%20treatment%20of%20Shudras.%20In%20%3Cem%3EMany%20Ramayanas%3A%20The%20Diversity%20of%20a%20Narrative%20Tradition%20in%20South%20Asia%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20author%20Paula%20Richman%20writes%20that%20Periyar%20summarised%20the%20killing%20of%20Shambuk%20and%20extrapolated%20from%20it%20to%20present-day%20South%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERichman%20wrote%3A%20%E2%80%9C%E2%80%99If%20there%20were%20kings%20like%20Rama%20now%2C%20what%20would%20be%20the%20fate%20of%20those%20people%20called%20Sudras%3F%E2%80%99%20he%20asks%2C%20implying%20that%20Sudras%20would%20never%20be%20safe%20from%20murder%20if%20such%20a%20king%20still%20ruled.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThrough%20references%20to%20Ambedkar%20and%20Periyar%E2%80%99s%20writings%20on%20the%20subject%2C%20Harijan%20defends%20the%20context%20of%20his%20controversial%20tweet.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20discuss%20all%20these%2C%20how%20will%20we%20teach%20the%20%3Cem%3EAnnihilation%20of%20Caste%3C%2Fem%3E%20to%20students%3F%20How%20will%20we%20bring%20an%20end%20to%20religious%20and%20caste%20rigidities%3F%20If%20I%20am%20wrong%2C%20then%20even%20Ambedkar%2C%20Periyar%20and%20Jyotiba%20Phule%20are%20wrong.%20They%20all%20raised%20such%20questions.%20What%20I%20have%20said%20is%20nothing%20new%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20Harijan%20later%20deleted%20his%20tweet%20on%20Ram%20and%20Krishna%2C%20he%20said%20he%20stands%20by%20the%20message%20he%20wanted%20to%20convey.%20His%20conviction%2C%20and%20disdain%20for%20caste%20and%20ills%20of%20the%20Hindu%20faith%2C%20are%20rooted%20in%20his%20lived%20experience%20as%20a%20Jatav%2FChamar%20(Dalit%20sub-caste)%20from%20an%20impoverished%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Not%20human%20enough%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHarijan%20was%20born%20in%20a%20village%20in%20Gorakhpur%20in%20eastern%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%20His%20grandmother%20used%20to%20cut%20umbilical%20cords%20of%20new-born%20babies.%20In%20return%2C%20she%20would%20have%20rotis%20thrown%20down%20at%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHarijan%E2%80%99s%20father%20worked%20as%20a%20harwah%20(full-time%20in-house%20labourer)%20who%20toiled%20both%20on%20the%20field%20as%20well%20as%20inside%20the%20house%20of%20the%20dominant%20caste%20zamindar.%20In%20return%2C%20he%20got%20food.%20But%20the%20quality%20of%20food%20was%20bad%20and%20the%20mistress%20of%20the%20house%20often%20served%20him%20left-overs.%20In%20the%20village%2C%20poor%20Dalit%20families%20like%20Harijan%E2%80%99s%20would%20often%20resort%20to%20eating%20gobrah%20roti%20to%20fill%20their%20stomach.%20These%20rotis%20were%20made%20from%20grains%20collected%20after%20washing%20cow%20dung.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnhappy%20with%20this%20setup%2C%20Harijan%E2%80%99s%20father%20left%20the%20work%20at%20the%20zamindar%E2%80%99s%20and%20migrated%20to%20West%20Bengal%2C%20where%20he%20got%20associated%20with%20the%20Naxalite%20movement.%20%E2%80%9CAs%20a%20worker%20of%20the%20Naxalite%20movement%2C%20he%20even%20made%20bombs%20for%20a%20while%2C%E2%80%9D%20recalled%20Harijan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20father%20then%20joined%20a%20coal%20mine%20in%20Asansol%20as%20a%20worker.%20The%20family%20lived%20in%20a%20colony%20with%20other%20migrant%20workers%20from%20UP%20and%20Bihar.%20Harijan%20spent%20his%20childhood%20in%20difficult%20circumstances.%20The%20colony%20did%20not%20provide%20him%20the%20atmosphere%20to%20study.%20In%20the%20evenings%2C%20men%20would%20play%20cards%2C%20get%20drunk%20or%20often%20get%20into%20fights.%20But%20the%20support%20he%20received%20from%20his%20school%20teachers%20ensured%20he%20stayed%20motivated%20to%20study.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Bengal%20he%20studied%20in%20a%20Hindi-medium%20government%20school%20from%20class%201%20to%2010.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHarijan%20also%20remembers%20that%20in%20Bengal%20he%20would%20often%20join%20other%20workers%20to%20steal%20coal%20from%20mines%20that%20had%20closed%20for%20business.%20He%20could%20relate%20it%20to%20his%20experience%20in%20his%20village%20in%20Gorakhpur%20where%20he%20often%20picked%20sugarcane%2C%20peas%20and%20sweet%20potato%20from%20other%E2%80%99s%20farms%20to%20beat%20hunger.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Harijan%E2%80%99s%20memories%20are%20not%20restricted%20to%20poverty%20and%20financial%20constraints.%20Growing%20up%20in%20faraway%20Bengal%2C%20too%2C%20he%20faced%20casteism%20and%20saw%20the%20caste%20divisions%20within%20the%20labourers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSome%20members%20of%20the%20Yadav%20and%20barber%20caste%20and%20even%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fbihar-caste-survey-the-whos-who-in-the-data-pasi%5C%22%3EPasis%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who%20are%20themselves%20Dalits%2C%20would%20pass%20casteist%20remarks%20at%20me%20about%20my%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fbihar-caste-survey-the-whos-who-in-the-data-chamar%5C%22%3EChamar%3C%2Fa%3E%20caste.%20A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fbihar-caste-survey-the-whos-who-in-the-data-yadav%5C%22%3EYadav%3C%2Fa%3E%20man%20would%20often%20tease%20me%20by%20distorting%20the%20popular%20song%20%E2%80%98O%E2%80%99maria%2C%20O%E2%80%99maria%E2%80%99%20to%20%E2%80%98O%E2%80%99Chamariya%2C%20O%E2%80%99%20Chamariya%E2%80%99%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Harijan.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20bullying%20was%20so%20normal%20that%20I%20had%20developed%20so%20much%20inferiority%20complex%20that%20I%20started%20to%20believe%20I%20was%20not%20human%20enough.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHarijan%20was%20in%20class%20six%20or%20seven%20when%20while%20reading%20a%20book%20on%20Buddha%20he%20started%20to%20wonder%20about%20untouchability%20and%20caste%20discrimination%20and%20related%20it%20to%20his%20life.%20The%20turning%20point%20came%20when%20an%20upper%20caste%20tuition%20teacher%20made%20casteist%20remarks%20against%20another%20Dalit%20student%20dismissing%20reservation%20as%20a%20charity%20served%20by%20tax%20money%20of%20upper%20castes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHarijan%20was%20offended%20by%20this%20and%20stood%20up%20for%20his%20classmate.%20However%2C%20for%20speaking%20up%2C%20he%20was%20thrown%20out%20of%20the%20class.%20The%20episode%20made%20him%20furious%20and%20he%20gradually%20stopped%20worshipping%20Hindu%20deities.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20incident%20made%20me%20rebel%20against%20Hindu%20faith%20and%20caste%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F27131715%2FIMG-20231122-WA0140.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F27131715%2FIMG-20231122-WA0140.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F27131715%2FIMG-20231122-WA0140-300x135.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F27131715%2FIMG-20231122-WA0140-1024x459.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-686530%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22538%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EVikram%20Harijan%20with%20his%20students.%20Photo%3A%20By%20arrangement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Backlash%20from%20a%20deity%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHarijan%20was%20still%20young%20and%20yet%20to%20discover%20the%20writings%20of%20Ambedkar%20and%20Periyar.%20His%20initial%20influence%20came%20in%20the%20form%20of%20reformist%20ideas%20of%20Raja%20Ram%20Mohan%20Roy%2C%20who%20had%20opposed%20idol%20worship%20and%20denounced%20the%20caste%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Harijan%20started%20opposing%20idol%20worship%2C%20he%20caused%20a%20stir%20among%20his%20classmates%20by%20refusing%20to%20give%20the%20customary%20donation%20for%20Saraswati%20Puja.%20Stunned%20by%20his%20defiance%2C%20his%20fellow%20students%20dared%20him%20to%20perform%20an%20outrageous%20dare%20to%20prove%20his%20conviction.%20They%20asked%20him%20to%20urinate%20on%20the%20idol%20of%20a%20Hindu%20deity.%20He%20went%20to%20a%20nearby%20temple%20and%20performed%20the%20act.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20incident%20from%20his%20childhood%20came%20back%20to%20haunt%20him%20in%202019%2C%20when%20he%20was%20already%20teaching%20at%20the%20Allahabad%20University.%20In%20August%20that%20year%2C%20a%20research%20scholar%2C%20also%20a%20Dalit%2C%20out%20of%20personal%20vendetta%20uploaded%20an%20old%20video%20of%20Harijan%20(recorded%20at%20a%20private%20event%20at%20a%20hostel%20on%20the%20occasion%20of%20Ambedkar%20Jayanti%20on%20April%2014%2C%202017)%20in%20which%20he%20brags%20how%20as%20a%20student%20he%20had%20insulted%20a%20Hindu%20deity%20by%20urinating%20over%20it%20but%20faced%20no%20backlash%20from%20the%20deity.%20Harijan%20said%20he%20narrated%20the%20experience%20to%20the%20students%20as%20he%20wanted%20to%20bust%20their%20fears%20associated%20with%20religion%20and%20divine%20punishment%2C%20and%20not%20to%20hurt%20religious%20sentiments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20university%20saw%20it%20differently%20and%20served%20him%20a%20notice%20following%20a%20complaint%20by%20a%20delegation%20of%20students%20who%20were%20offended%20by%20his%20comments.%20A%20student%20of%20the%20Akhil%20Bharatiya%20Vidhyarthi%20Parishad%20even%20lodged%20a%20police%20complaint%20against%20him.%20Following%20the%20uproar%20over%20his%20comments%2C%20Harijan%20feared%20he%20could%20be%20lynched%20and%20even%20requested%20authorities%20to%20grant%20him%20protection.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHarijan%20completed%20his%20intermediate%20schooling%20from%20Gorakhpur%20and%20graduated%20from%20Gorakhpur%20University%2C%20before%20completing%20his%20PhD%20from%20the%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20University%20on%20%E2%80%98Occupational%20caste%20groups%20and%20English%20east%20India%20company%20in%20Madras%20during%2017%20and%2018%20centuries%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20Allahabad%20University%2C%20he%20also%20teaches%20about%20marginalised%20communities%20in%20Indian%20history%20and%20includes%20text%20on%20caste%2C%20Ambedkar%2C%20Phule%20and%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENotices%20and%20a%20space%20for%20discussion%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20January%202021%2C%20he%20wrote%20a%20letter%20to%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20welcoming%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20step%20to%20remove%20caste%20names%20from%20vehicles%2C%20and%20requested%20him%20to%20issue%20guidelines%20to%20remove%20caste%20names%20prefixed%20and%20suffixed%20on%20the%20shops%20of%20public%20and%20private%20shops%20and%20industries.%20As%20examples%2C%20he%20cited%20Aggarwal%20Sweets%2C%20Jaiswal%20Cloth%20Bhandar%2C%20Pandit%20Kachuri%2C%20etc.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20October%202021%2C%20the%20National%20Commission%20for%20Scheduled%20Castes%20took%20cognisance%20of%20a%20news%20report%20in%20which%20Harijan%20had%20claimed%20that%20there%20was%20caste%20discrimination%20on%20campus%20and%20that%20marks%20were%20given%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20caste.%20The%20varsity%20asked%20him%20to%20explain%20the%20basis%20of%20allegations%20along%20with%20documentary%20proof.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20varsity%20had%20also%20issued%20him%20a%20show%20cause%20notice%20after%20he%20sent%20a%20representation%20to%20the%20NCSC%20regarding%20alleged%20mental%20harassment%20and%20discrimination%20by%20AU.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHarijan%20feels%20there%20is%20little%20space%20to%20debate%20and%20discuss%20complex%20issues%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20rigidity%20and%20taboo%20in%20religions.%20It%E2%80%99s%20essential%20to%20question%20rigidities%20in%20all%20faiths%2C%20be%20it%20Hindu%2C%20Islam%2C%20Sikh%20or%20others%2C%20he%20argues.%20%E2%80%9CWhat%20was%20the%20Indian%20constitution%20made%20for%20if%20not%20to%20provide%20space%20for%20these%20discussions%20that%20formed%20the%20basis%20for%20similar%20movements%20and%20revolutions%20in%20France%2C%20Russia%2C%20England%20and%20USA%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThose%20offended%20by%20Harijan%E2%80%99s%20views%20often%20accuse%20him%20of%20selectively%20targeting%20Hindu%20faith.%20He%20said%20he%20talks%20more%20about%20the%20rigidities%20of%20the%20Hindu%20religion%20as%20he%20was%20born%20into%20it.%20%E2%80%9CI%20talk%20about%20the%20Hindu%20religion%20because%20Hindu%20dharm%20made%20me%20a%20Chamar.%20It%20made%20me%20eat%20gobrah%20roti%20as%20a%20child.%20My%20first%20fight%20is%20against%20the%20caste%20structure%20of%20Hinduism%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20landing%20in%20controversy%20and%20finding%20himself%20in%20the%20radar%20of%20a%20Hindu%20nationalist%20government%2C%20Harijan%20is%20defiant.%20He%20feels%20it%20is%20his%20right%20to%20educate%20the%20people%20of%20the%20Bahujan%20Samaj%20about%20systemic%20caste%20oppression%2C%20and%20infuse%20rationality%2C%20scientific%20thinking%20and%20ideas%20of%20enlightenment%20in%20his%20students.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20should%20not%20escape%20discussion%20through%20the%20hollow%20excuse%20of%20hurt%20religious%20sentiments%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Harijan%2C%20who%20has%20on%20many%20occasions%20expressed%20threat%20to%20his%20life%2C%20fears%20he%20might%20face%20the%20same%20fate%20as%20other%20rationalists%20such%20as%20Govind%20Pansare.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20may%20be%20shot%20dead%20for%20my%20views.%20But%20what%20is%20the%20meaning%20of%20being%20educated%20if%20I%20cannot%20stand%20up%20for%20rationality.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701071347000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F27131120%2FIMG-20231122-WA0134.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fvikram-harijan-allahabad-university-hindu-deities%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Allahabad%20University%20professor%20is%20battling%20police%20cases%2C%20varsity%20raps%20on%20his%20knuckles%20and%20volleys%20of%20harassment%20over%20his%20comments%20against%20the%20caste%20structure%20of%20Hinduism.%20But%20he%20is%20unrelenting.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A14%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fvikram-harijan-allahabad-university-hindu-deities%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Record%20numbers%20sit%20for%20China%20civil%20service%20exam%2C%20hoping%20for%20job%20security%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701070773000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-105529490%2Cimgsize-108918.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fchina%2Frecord-numbers-sit-for-china-civil-service-exam-hoping-for-job-security%2Farticleshow%2F105528810.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F105528810.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3E%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fchina%2Frecord-numbers-sit-for-china-civil-service-exam-hoping-for-job-security%2Farticleshow%2F105528810.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm-timesofindia-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fchina%2Frecord-numbers-sit-for-china-civil-service-exam-hoping-for-job-security%2Famp_articleshow%2F105528810.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fchina%2Frecord-numbers-sit-for-china-civil-service-exam-hoping-for-job-security%2Famp_articleshow%2F105528810.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Chief%20Justice%20Bats%20For%20Inclusivity%2C%20Spotlights%20%26quot%3BBias%26quot%3B%20In%20English-Only%20CLAT%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EChief%20Justice%20of%20India%20D%20Y%20Chandrachud%20on%20Sunday%20said%20that%20there%20should%20be%20greater%20participation%20of%20women%20in%20the%20higher%20judiciary%20and%20emphasised%20the%20need%20for%20a%20more%20inclusive%20legal%20profession.%20He%20underscored%20the%20importance%20of%20increased%20engagement%20with%20members%20of%20underprivileged%20and%20marginalised%20communities.%20Speaking%20at%20an%20event%20celebrating%20Bhimrao%20Ambedkar's%20100%20years%20of%20legal%20practice%2C%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20appealed%20to%20the%20legal%20community%20to%20support%20Ambedkar's%20vision%20of%20equality%20in%20all%20spheres%20of%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20urged%20judges%20from%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20high%20courts%2C%20and%20senior%20advocates%20to%20contemplate%20ways%20to%20enhance%20inclusivity%20within%20the%20legal%20profession.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHighlighting%20that%20individuals%20from%20marginalised%20communities%20may%20not%20be%20proficient%20in%20English%2C%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20discussed%20the%20Common%20Law%20Admission%20Tests%20(CLAT)%2C%20emphasising%20that%20it%20is%20exclusively%20administered%20in%20English.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20CLAT%20examination%2C%20a%20crucial%20gateway%20to%20the%20legal%20profession%2C%20is%20conducted%20entirely%20in%20English.%20By%20using%20English%20as%20the%20medium%20of%20examination%2C%20we%20are%20essentially%20favouring%20an%20urban-centric%20approach%20and%20creating%20a%20significant%20bias%20against%20individuals%20from%20rural%20or%20marginalised%20backgrounds%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%C2%A0Chief%20Justice.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20this%20matter%2C%20a%20Public%20Interest%20Litigation%20(PIL)%20awaits%20resolution%20in%20the%20Delhi%20High%20Court%2C%20advocating%20for%20the%20administration%20of%20the%20CLAT%20in%20regional%20languages.%20The%20Bar%20Council%20of%20India%20has%20recently%20endorsed%20the%20idea%20of%20conducting%20the%20CLAT%20in%20regional%20languages%20and%20has%20offered%20to%20organise%20the%20test.%20Additionally%2C%20the%20National%20Testing%20Agency%20has%20informed%20the%20High%20Court%20that%20it%20can%20conduct%20the%20CLAT%20in%20regional%20languages.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20CJI%20Chandrachud%20condemned%20the%20biased%20practice%20of%20only%20selecting%20clerks%20from%20national%20law%20schools%20and%20detailed%20the%20preparation%2C%20submission%2C%20and%20implementation%20of%20a%20white%20paper%20aimed%20at%20reorienting%20the%20clerkship%20programme.%20He%20also%20discussed%20the%20joint%20efforts%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20and%20the%20National%20Commission%20for%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20(NCST)%20to%20introduce%20structured%20and%20modulated%20internship%20programs.%20These%20programmes%20were%20designed%20to%20address%20concerns%20expressed%20by%20the%20NCST%20regarding%20the%20lack%20of%20activities%20available%20to%20students%20from%20tribal%20communities.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701070500000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-11%2Fhoq203p_cji-dy-chandrachud_625x300_20_November_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Feducation%2Fclats-english-only-format-excludes-rural-marginalised-aspirants-chief-justice-dy-chandrachud-4609398%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20D%20Y%20Chandrachud%20urged%20judges%20from%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20high%20courts%2C%20and%20senior%20advocates%20to%20contemplate%20ways%20to%20enhance%20inclusivity%20within%20the%20legal%20profession.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Feducation%2Fclats-english-only-format-excludes-rural-marginalised-aspirants-chief-justice-dy-chandrachud-4609398%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Feducation%2Fclats-english-only-format-excludes-rural-marginalised-aspirants-chief-justice-dy-chandrachud-4609398%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Feducation%2Fclats-english-only-format-excludes-rural-marginalised-aspirants-chief-justice-dy-chandrachud-4609398%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Bihar%3A%20Nitish%20Kumar%20Asks%20Officials%20to%20Conduct%20Survey%20on%20Impact%20of%20Prohibition%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F27125235%2F400885315_926965215455506_1904449686751089128_n.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%C2%A0Bihar%20chief%20minister%20Nitish%20Kumar%20on%20Sunday%20asked%20officials%20to%20conduct%20a%20door-to-door%20survey%20to%20study%20the%20impact%20of%20alcohol%20prohibition%2C%20imposed%20by%20his%20government%20seven%20years%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Findia%2Fbihar%2Fstory%2Fnitish-calls-for-fresh-survey-to-study-impact-of-prohibition-in-bihar-2467868-2023-11-27%5C%22%3Enews%20agency%20PTI%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Kumar%20made%20these%20remarks%20at%20an%20event%20on%20%E2%80%98Nashamukti%20Diwas%E2%80%99%20(Deaddiction%20Day)%2C%20which%20is%20observed%20every%20November%2026.%20Bihar%20imposed%20total%20prohibition%20in%20April%202016%2C%20banning%20the%20manufacture%2C%20trade%2C%20storage%2C%20possession%20and%20consumption%20of%20all%20types%20of%20liquor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraphindia.com%2Findia%2Fbihar-chief-minister-nitish-kumar-asks-officials-to-conduct-a-door-to-door-survey-on-prohibition-impact%2Fcid%2F1982803%5C%22%3EAccording%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Telegraph%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Kumar%20said%20that%20a%20survey%20conducted%20in%202018%20to%20study%20the%20impact%20of%20prohibition%20revealed%20that%20%E2%80%9C1.64%20crore%20people%20in%20the%20state%20quit%20drinking%2C%20while%20another%20done%20in%202023%20brought%20to%20light%20that%201.82%20crore%20people%20have%20stopped%20consuming%20liquor%E2%80%9D.%20It%20showed%20that%2099%25%20of%20women%20and%2092%25%20of%20men%20in%20Bihar%20were%20in%20favour%20of%20prohibition%2C%20the%20chief%20minister%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20per%20the%20survey%2C%20the%20loss%20in%20revenue%20was%20more%20than%20offset%20by%20the%20money%20people%20were%20saving%20and%20spending%20on%20improving%20their%20economic%20condition%20and%20ensuring%20better%20education%20for%20their%20children.%20Besides%2C%20there%20are%20studies%20by%20the%20World%20Health%20Organisation%20which%20enlist%20harmful%20effects%20of%20alcohol%20consumption%2C%20including%20fatal%20road%20accidents%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20chief%20minister%20said%2C%20indicating%20that%20the%20ban%20would%20not%20be%20lifted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20would%20urge%20the%20people%20here%20to%20consider%20a%20fresh%20survey%20which%20would%20give%20a%20fresh%20estimate%20of%20the%20impact%20of%20prohibition.%20Based%20on%20the%20findings%2C%20we%20would%20introduce%20fresh%20measures.%20But%20I%20must%20make%20it%20clear%20that%20prohibition%20is%20there%20to%20stay%2C%20for%20as%20long%20as%20I%20am%20in%20charge%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701070171000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F27125235%2F400885315_926965215455506_1904449686751089128_n.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fbihar-nitish-kumar-survey-impact-prohibition%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20chief%20minister%20said%20that%20the%20loss%20in%20revenue%20due%20to%20the%20liquor%20ban%20was%20more%20than%20offset%20by%20the%20money%20people%20were%20saving%20and%20spending%20on%20improving%20their%20economic%20condition%20and%20ensuring%20better%20education.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fbihar-nitish-kumar-survey-impact-prohibition%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22It%20Is%20Time%20Cricket%20Moves%20Past%20Silly%20Notions%20Of%20%E2%80%98Winning%20DNA%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98Choking%20Gene%E2%80%99%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F27121214%2FF_NTX9lbYAAsGNV-1080x600-1.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESporting%20mythology%20is%20funny.%20It%20often%20at%20the%20same%20time%20means%20different%20things%20to%20different%20people.%20It%E2%80%99s%20rooted%20in%20some%20strongly%20held%20cultural%20cliches%2C%20a%20few%20lazy%20stereotypes%2C%20and%20a%20very%20peculiar%20human%20need%20to%20make%20sense%20of%20an%20outcome%20that%E2%80%99s%20mostly%20the%20result%20of%20a%20completely%20random%20set%20of%20events.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20mythologising%20involves%20a%20fundamentally%20incorrect%20understanding%20of%20how%20a%20sporting%20contest%20between%20roughly%20equal%20opponents%20works.%20It%20assumes%20a%20given%20outcome%20is%20the%20result%20of%20something%20deeper%20than%20what%E2%80%99s%20apparent.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGiven%20the%20level%20of%20emotional%20attachment%20fans%20follow%20a%20contest%20with%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20somewhat%20hard%20to%20stomach%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20result%20is%20entirely%20determined%20by%20events%20on%20the%20field%3B%20and%20that%20the%20slightest%20change%20in%20some%20in-game%20variables%20could%E2%80%99ve%20forced%20an%20opposite%20outcome.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20that%E2%80%99s%20an%20inherent%20limitation%20of%20outcome-oriented%20analysis.%20It%20fails%20to%20both%20account%20for%20and%20adequately%20understand%20the%20principle%20of%20randomness%20%E2%80%93%20arguably%20the%20biggest%20determinant%20of%20margins%20within%20which%20a%20match%20is%20won%20or%20lost.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESince%20sport%20in%20modern%20times%20is%20mostly%20consumed%20on%20television%20and%20the%20medium%20requires%20it%20to%20be%20presented%20with%20a%20certain%20tonality%20for%20effect%2C%20the%20audience%20has%20grown%20increasingly%20desperate%20to%20find%20explanations%20for%20a%20team%E2%80%99s%20performance%20in%20meaningless%20intangibles.%20Tags%20like%20%E2%80%98serial%20winners%E2%80%99%2C%20%E2%80%98chokers%E2%80%99%2C%20%E2%80%98stepping-up-when-it-matters%E2%80%99%20are%20thrown%20about%20loosely%20and%20television%20commentary%20that%20assists%20a%20fan%E2%80%99s%20viewing%20experience%20does%20everything%20in%20its%20power%20to%20solidify%20these%20notions.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20this%20tendency%20is%20prevalent%20across%20all%20major%20sports%2C%20cricket%20perhaps%20takes%20the%20crown%20for%20allowing%20these%20empty%20labels%20to%20completely%20hijack%20the%20discourse.%20The%20Australians%2C%20in%20this%20universe%20of%20fanciful%20imaginations%2C%20are%20supposed%20to%20have%20the%20genetic%20code%20to%20win%20tournaments%20with%20their%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fcricketworldcup%2Fstatus%2F1726758248299061491%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ewinners%E2%80%99%20DNA%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Cspan%3Ewhile%20India%20on%20the%20other%20hand%20are%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Fsports%2Fworld-cup-chokers-india-searches-for-answers-after-latest-letdown%2Farticleshow%2F105350361.cms%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eperennial%20chokers%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20now%2C%20having%20upstaged%20South%20Africa%20%E2%80%93%20who%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcricket%2Fworld-cup%2Fcurse-of-the-knockouts-south-africa-s-choking-history-at-the-world-cups-123111600193_1.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eheld%20on%20to%20this%20(dubious)%20title%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20for%20the%20better%20part%20of%20cricket%E2%80%99s%20television%20age.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20World%20Cup%20final%20in%20Ahmedabad%2C%20where%20Australia%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ecomprehensively%20beat%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20India%20in%20front%20of%20a%20jampacked%20Narendra%20Modi%20Stadium%2C%20reignited%20this%20discourse%20again.%20The%20final%20was%20supposed%20to%20be%20the%20culmination%20point%20of%20the%20perfect%20Indian%20dream.%20The%20team%20had%20entered%20the%20final%20as%20firm%20favourites%2C%20having%20won%20ten%20games%20on%20the%20bounce.%20Australia%20on%20the%20other%20hand%20had%20started%20slow%2C%20struggled%20to%20find%20their%20best%20combination%20and%20almost%20made%20a%20mess%20of%20what%20should%E2%80%99ve%20been%20a%20straightforward%20chase%20in%20the%20semifinal.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20their%20ten-match%20winning%20streak%2C%20India%20encountered%20every%20possible%20game%20scenario%20and%20came%20out%20unscathed.%20Their%20bowlers%20constantly%20restricted%20teams%20to%20below-par%20totals%20when%20bowling%20first%20on%20slow%20tracks%20and%20at%20the%20same%20time%2C%20batting%20teams%20out%20of%20the%20contest%20on%20flat%20pitches%20was%20no%20trouble%20either.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESkipper%20Rohit%20Sharma%20batted%20with%20unmatched%20flair%20and%20put%20the%20team%20in%20a%20position%20of%20dominance%20game%20after%20game.%20Virat%20Kohli%20cracked%20the%20perfect%20pace%20for%20the%20middle%20order%20to%20bat%20around%20him%20for%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20innings.%20And%20few%20had%20answers%20to%20deal%20with%20the%20fast-bowling%20menace%20of%20Jasprit%20Bumrah%20and%20Mohammed%20Shami.%20What%20exactly%20was%20there%20to%20stop%20the%20Indian%20juggernaut%20other%20than%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ebig%20game%20pressure%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Ethe%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Efear%20of%20failure%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Eand%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eburden%20of%20expectations%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%20%7C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsport%2Fcricket-mata-ki-jai-jingoism-lost-in-ahmedabad-on-sunday%5C%22%3ECricket%20Mata%20Ki%20Jai%3A%20Jingoism%20Lost%20in%20Ahmedabad%20on%20Sunday%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESadly%2C%20the%20outcome%20of%20a%20game%20of%20cricket%20for%20the%20most%20part%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20have%20too%20much%20to%20do%20with%20any%20of%20the%20above%20and%20instead%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Edoes%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20have%20too%20much%20to%20do%20with%20that%2022-yard%20strip%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20ground.%20On%20a%20sluggish%20surface%20where%20it%E2%80%99s%20hard%20to%20trust%20the%20pace%20and%20bounce%20of%20the%20ball%2C%20India%20were%20at%20a%20considerable%20disadvantage%20having%20to%20bat%20first%20after%20losing%20the%20toss.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBarring%20Sharma%20and%20to%20an%20extent%20Kohli%2C%20every%20Indian%20batsman%20struggled%20to%20time%20the%20ball%20and%20Australia%E2%80%99s%20meticulously%20planned%20bowling%20tactics%20didn%E2%80%99t%20help%20much%20either.%20Sure%2C%20the%20gravity%20of%20the%20final%20did%20play%20its%20part%3B%20in%20that%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20hard%20to%20imagine%20India%20scoring%20all%20of%20four%20boundaries%20over%20a%2040-over%20stretch%20on%20a%20lesser%20occasion%20with%20their%20legacies%20not%20being%20written%20about%20in%20real-time.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%E2%80%99s%20fair%20to%20assume%20the%20Indian%20middle%20order%20may%20perhaps%20have%20taken%20a%20few%20more%20risks%20and%20pushed%20the%20score%20more%20than%20they%20did%20were%20it%20not%20for%20the%20hype%20around%20what%20was%20arguably%20the%20biggest%20match%20of%20their%20careers.%20It%E2%80%99s%20impossible%20to%20imagine%20two%20part-timers%20(Mitchell%20Marsh%20and%20Travis%20Head)%20getting%20away%20with%20four%20overs%20between%20them%20conceding%20only%20nine%20on%20any%20other%20day.%20But%20there%E2%80%99s%20only%20so%20much%20these%20psychological%20factors%20influence%20the%20course%20of%20a%20game%20between%20two%20high-quality%20teams.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20indeed%20was%20the%20stark%20contrast%20in%20playing%20conditions%20in%20the%20final%20from%20the%20earlier%20stages%20of%20the%20tournament%20that%20completely%20stagnated%20India%E2%80%99s%20scoring%20rate%20and%20kept%20them%20well%20short%20of%20what%20would%E2%80%99ve%20been%20a%20challenging%20total.%20Having%20to%20chase%20a%20modest%20score%20by%20modern%20standards%20and%20batting%20on%20a%20fairly%20settled%20pitch%20under%20lights%2C%20Australia%20made%20light%20work%20of%20the%20target.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Australian%20bowlers%20didn%E2%80%99t%20fluster%20despite%20the%20early%20onslaught%20by%20India%20and%20stuck%20to%20their%20plan%20of%20denying%20the%20batters%20any%20pace%20on%20the%20ball%20by%20constantly%20bowling%20into%20the%20pitch.%20Captain%20Pat%20Cummins%20in%20particular%20had%20a%20day%20he%20will%20never%20tire%20of%20talking%20about%20for%20the%20rest%20of%20his%20life.%20But%20to%20ignore%20the%20competitive%20advantage%20he%20gained%20at%20the%20toss%20on%20that%20day%20would%20be%20a%20dishonest%20appraisal%20of%20his%20effort.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20chase%20was%20even%20funnier.%20The%20entire%20top%20order%20came%20with%20a%20plan%20to%20throw%20their%20hands%20against%20anything%20remotely%20wide%20while%20the%20ball%20was%20hard%20and%20came%20decently%20onto%20the%20bat.%20David%20Warner%20and%20Mitchell%20Marsh%20perished%20to%20this%20philosophy%20while%20Travis%20Head%20managed%20to%20survive%20despite%20no%20discernibly%20different%20technique%20and%20lived%20to%20tell%20the%20tale%20of%20his%20heroics.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESure%2C%20Head%20went%20on%20to%20ruthlessly%20dominate%20the%20Indian%20bowling%20once%20the%20ball%20stopped%20moving%20as%20viciously%20but%20his%20survival%20to%20that%20point%20involved%20an%20insane%20amount%20of%20luck%20%E2%80%93%20not%20some%20mentality%20potion%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Estand%20up%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%20%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ewhen%20it%20counts%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20the%20Australians%20have%20secretly%20gotten%20hold%20of.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%E2%80%99s%20a%20very%20clear%20and%20coherent%20cricketing%20explanation%20that%20highlights%20the%20difference%20in%20how%20the%20two%20teams%20performed%20in%20the%20final.%20But%20to%20attribute%20the%20result%20entirely%20to%20a%20fairly%20unintelligent%20and%20rudimentary%20understanding%20of%20cultures%20is%20laughably%20reductive.%20The%20cricket%20media%20and%20commentary%20teams%2C%20however%2C%20wholeheartedly%20indulge%20in%20this%20exercise.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F20173049%2FF_UEPDVXgAAmcLH.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F20173049%2FF_UEPDVXgAAmcLH.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F20173049%2FF_UEPDVXgAAmcLH-300x158.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F20173049%2FF_UEPDVXgAAmcLH-1024x540.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-685550%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22633%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EPat%20Cummins%20celebrates%20after%20winning%20the%202023%20Cricket%20World%20Cup.%20Photo%3A%20Twitter%2F%40cricketworldcup%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWeak%20narratives%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMuch%20of%20cricket%E2%80%99s%20punditry%20today%20borrows%20their%20perceptions%20of%20Australia%20from%20the%20indomitable%20team%20under%20Steve%20Waugh%20and%20Ricky%20Ponting%20that%20bagged%20three%20World%20Cup%20titles%20on%20the%20trot.%20While%20the%20aura%20of%20that%20team%20indeed%20was%20extremely%20intimidating%2C%20the%20dominance%20was%20simply%20down%20to%20them%20being%20remarkably%20better%20than%20everyone%20else.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20even%20if%20it%E2%80%99s%20conceded%20that%20cricketing%20prepotency%20lent%20them%20some%20mental%20edge%20over%20opponents%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20fatuous%20to%20assume%20that%20mentality%20transcends%20across%20eras%20and%20that%20an%20Australian%20team%20today%20%E2%80%93%20with%20no%20trace%20whatsoever%20to%20that%20one%20%E2%80%93%20continues%20to%20be%20of%20similar%20mental%20makeup.%20The%20implication%20is%20insincere%20and%20borders%20on%20a%20belief%20in%20racial%20supremacy.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESimilarly%2C%20the%20narrative%20formed%20around%20the%20current%20Indian%20team%20is%20on%20equally%20thin%20grounds.%20That%20India%20has%20failed%20to%20win%20a%20relevant%20trophy%20in%20limited-overs%20tournaments%20for%20ten%20years%20now%20is%20linked%20to%20the%20team%E2%80%99s%20failure%20to%20handle%20pressure%20in%20high-profile%20knockout%20games.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsport%2Findia-australia-cricket-world-cup-final-gideon-haigh%5C%22%3EIn%20the%20End%2C%20It%E2%80%99s%20Always%20XI%20Versus%20XI%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20very%20cursory%20glance%20at%20these%20handful%20of%20games%20would%20reveal%20India%20got%20outclassed%20at%20least%20twice%20by%20decisively%20better%20oppositions%20(Australia%20in%20the%202015%20ODI%20World%20Cup%2C%20and%20England%20in%20the%202022%20T20%20World%20Cup).%20In%20the%202019%20ODI%20World%20Cup%2C%20the%20conditions%20suited%20New%20Zealand%E2%80%99s%20seam%20bowling%20perfectly%2C%20whereas%20India%20paid%20a%20heavy%20price%20for%20losing%20the%20toss%20in%20their%20defeats%20to%20Sri%20Lanka%20and%20West%20Indies%20in%20the%202014%20and%202016%20T20%20World%20Cups%20respectively.%20The%202017%20Champions%20Trophy%20thrashing%20to%20Pakistan%20is%20the%20only%20one%20hard%20to%20explain%20in%20plain%20cricketspeak%20but%20that%20it%20was%20an%20anomaly%20is%20sufficiently%20proved%20by%20India%E2%80%99s%20treatment%20of%20Pakistan%20in%20ODIs%20on%20either%20side%20of%20that%20game.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20two%20World%20Test%20Championship%20(WTC)%20final%20defeats%20are%20now%20added%20to%20the%20list%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20glorious%20big-stage%20failures.%20This%20argument%20perhaps%20stands%20on%20the%20weakest%20legs%2C%20not%20that%20the%20others%20are%20particularly%20sound.%20The%20WTC%20final%20is%20a%20one-off%20exhibition%20Test%20match%20played%20in%20conditions%20where%20India%20starts%20at%20a%20massive%20disadvantage%20against%20the%20teams%20it%E2%80%99s%20realistically%20likely%20to%20face.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20current%20Indian%20Test%20team%E2%80%99s%20two%20series%20wins%20in%20Australia%20are%20a%20far%20bigger%20accomplishment%20than%20a%20WTC%20title%2C%20literally%20invented%20to%20infuse%20artificial%20excitement%20in%20Test%20cricket.%20Winning%20a%20single%20Test%20in%20Australia%20is%20objectively%20harder%20than%20qualifying%20for%20and%20winning%20the%20Test%20championship.%20For%20India%20to%20have%20won%20a%20series%20and%20repeat%20that%20again%20is%20a%20generational%20achievement.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENone%20of%20this%20is%20to%20suggest%20fans%20should%20have%20no%20qualms%20over%20India%E2%80%99s%20lack%20of%20silverware.%20But%20to%20imply%20they%20lack%20the%20bottle%20to%20deliver%20on%20the%20proverbial%20big%20day%20is%20both%20amateurish%20and%20lacks%20a%20nuanced%20understanding%20of%20sport.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECertainly%2C%20players%20experience%20greater%20pressure%20to%20perform%20on%20big%20occasions.%20This%20may%20show%20up%20in%20a%20more%20guarded%20and%20tentative%20approach%20they%20take.%20Batsmen%20may%20carry%20more%20self-doubt%20to%20execute%20some%20risky%20shots.%20But%20much%20like%20most%20games%20of%20cricket%2C%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ebig%20ones%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20too%20swing%20one%20way%20or%20the%20other%20based%20on%20the%20same%20set%20of%20variables%20%E2%80%93%20pitch%2C%20conditions%2C%20toss%2C%20and%20some%20happenstance.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20was%20nothing%20about%20Virat%20Kohli%E2%80%99s%20game%20that%20explained%20the%20returns%20of%209%2C%201%2C%20and%201%20in%20the%20three%20World%20Cup%20semifinals%20he%E2%80%99d%20played%20before%20the%202023%20edition.%20And%20even%20a%20magnificent%20hundred%20in%20his%20fourth%20attempt%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20guarantee%20he%20could%20be%20dismissed%20cheaply%20in%20the%20next%20one%20%E2%80%93%20should%20he%20make%20it%20that%20far%20again.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701069646000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F27121214%2FF_NTX9lbYAAsGNV-1080x600-1.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsport%2Fcricket-notions-winning-dna-choking-gene-world-cup%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20big%20games%20too%20swing%20one%20way%20or%20the%20other%20based%20on%20the%20same%20set%20of%20variables%20%E2%80%93%20pitch%2C%20conditions%2C%20toss%2C%20and%20some%20happenstance.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsport%2Fcricket-notions-winning-dna-choking-gene-world-cup%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Beijing%20frets%20over%20Taiwan%20opposition%20split%20as%20parties%20go%20on%20the%20attack%20over%20China%20ties%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701069610000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-105529043%2Cimgsize-44664.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fchina%2Fbeijing-frets-over-taiwan-opposition-split-as-parties-go-on-the-attack-over-china-ties%2Farticleshow%2F105529007.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F105529007.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EChina%20worries%20about%20split%20in%20Taiwan's%20opposition%2C%20boosting%20ruling%20DPP%20party.%20China's%20pressure%20on%20Taiwan%20escalates%20ahead%20of%20Jan.%2013%20election.%20Talks%20for%20united%20opposition%20ticket%20collapse%2C%20benefiting%20the%20DPP.%20Chinese%20social%20media%20laments%20opposition's%20disunity.%20DPP%20defies%20Chinese%20pressure%3B%20Lai%20Ching-te%20labeled%20a%20separatist.%20Mixed%20opinion%20polls%20show%20Lai%20with%20slight%20lead.%20Split%20opposition%20increases%20DPP's%20chance%20of%20victory%20in%20first-past-the-post%20system.%20DPP%20won%202020%20elections%20in%20a%20landslide%20against%20KMT's%20Han%20Kuo-yu.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fchina%2Fbeijing-frets-over-taiwan-opposition-split-as-parties-go-on-the-attack-over-china-ties%2Farticleshow%2F105529007.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm-timesofindia-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fchina%2Fbeijing-frets-over-taiwan-opposition-split-as-parties-go-on-the-attack-over-china-ties%2Famp_articleshow%2F105529007.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fchina%2Fbeijing-frets-over-taiwan-opposition-split-as-parties-go-on-the-attack-over-china-ties%2Famp_articleshow%2F105529007.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Caste%20Equality%20Advocates%20in%20the%20US%20Vow%20Not%20to%20Give%20Up%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F27114342%2Fimage-1548.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Prem%20Pariyar%20arrived%20in%20the%20United%20States%20from%20Nepal%20in%202015%2C%20he%20didn%E2%80%99t%20expect%20that%20he%20would%20be%20sleeping%20in%20a%20van%20or%20on%20couches%20in%C2%A0employee%20housing%20due%20to%20his%20caste%20affiliation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20thought%20caste%20discrimination%20does%20not%20exist%20here.%20I%20was%20very%20depressed%2C%E2%80%9D%20Pariyar%20told%20%3Cem%3EDW.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPariyar%2C%20a%20descendant%20of%20a%20family%20in%20the%20Hindu%20Dalit%20caste%2C%20sometimes%20referred%20to%20discriminatorily%20as%20the%20%E2%80%9CUntouchables%2C%E2%80%9D%C2%A0is%20one%20of%20many%20South%20Asian%20advocates%20pushing%20forward%20efforts%20to%20legally%20recognize%20caste%20discrimination%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Funited-states-of-america%2Ft-19065189%5C%22%3Ethe%20US%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20caste%20is%20commonly%20referred%20to%20in%20the%20context%20of%20Hinduism%20and%20India%2C%20it%20is%20a%20social%20hierarchy%20system%20that%20is%20thousands%20of%20years%20old%20and%20recognized%20in%20several%20countries%20across%20the%20region%2C%20including%20Nepal%2C%20where%20Pariyar%20grew%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20need%20to%20educate%20everyone%20so%20that%20this%20system%20will%20be%20stopped%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20told%20%3Cem%3EDW%3C%2Fem%3E.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20isolated%20generation%20to%20generation.%20There%20is%20intergenerational%20trauma.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECaste%20discrimination%20crossing%20borders%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPariyar%20decided%20to%20come%20to%20the%20US%20after%20his%20family%20was%20violently%20attacked%20because%20of%20their%20caste%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20night%20in%20their%20home%20in%20the%20Nepalese%C2%A0capital%2C%20Kathmandu.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20he%20tried%20to%20file%20charges%20against%20the%20assailant%2C%20the%20authorities%20did%20nothing%2C%20and%20even%20threatened%20him%20for%20taking%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPariyar%C2%A0proceeded%20to%20find%20a%20job%20at%20a%20restaurant%20in%20the%20US%2C%20where%20his%20employer%20offered%20to%20house%20him.%20However%2C%20his%20colleagues%20in%20the%20house%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20share%20a%20room%20with%20him%2C%20making%20casteist%20claims%20and%20slurs.%20So%2C%20he%20slept%20on%20the%20couch%C2%A0instead.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPariyar%2C%20who%20is%20now%20on%20the%20board%20of%20directors%20for%20the%20California%20chapter%20of%20the%20National%20Association%20of%20Social%20Workers%2C%20said%20his%20story%20is%20not%20unique.%20While%20he%20had%20hoped%20to%20leave%20this%20form%20of%20discrimination%20behind%20in%20Nepal%2C%20he%20said%20he%20and%20several%20others%20have%20faced%20significant%20hurdles%20in%20employment%20and%20even%20safety%20upon%20coming%20to%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20over%205.4%20million%20South%20Asians%20in%20the%20US%2C%20with%20the%20majority%20concentrated%20in%20California.%20They%20are%20one%20of%20the%20largest%20growing%20demographic%20groups%20in%20the%20country%2C%20with%20many%20people%20coming%20to%20work%20in%20the%20tech%20industry%20in%20California%E2%80%99s%20Silicon%20Valley.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20US-based%20Dalits%20have%20said%20the%20system%20of%20discrimination%20has%20followed%20them%2C%20resulting%20in%20harassment%2C%20sabotage%20in%20the%20workplace%20and%20even%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20recent%20years%2C%20activists%20have%20united%20under%20new%20groups%20such%20as%20the%20Californians%20for%20Caste%20Equity%20Coalition%20and%20Equality%20Labs%2C%C2%A0both%20instrumental%20in%20the%20push%20for%20legal%20recognitions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cstrong%3ELegal%20setback%20after%20California%20vetoes%20bill%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20October%2C%20following%20over%20a%20year%20of%20advocacy%20and%20a%20monthlong%20hunger%20strike%20by%20supporters%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fcalifornia-governor-scraps-bill-against-caste-discrimination%2Fa-67030645%5C%22%3ECalifornia%20Governor%20Gavin%20Newsom%20vetoed%20Senate%20Bill%20403%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20would%20have%20made%20the%20state%20the%20first%20to%20include%20caste%20in%20the%20list%20of%20protected%20classes%20under%20civil%20rights%20laws.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bill%20would%20have%20offered%20employment%20and%20housing%20protections%20alongside%20categories%20such%20as%20race%2C%20gender%20and%20sexual%20orientation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20despite%20an%20overwhelming%20majority%20(31-5%20in%20the%20Senate)%2C%20Newsom%20called%20the%20bill%20%E2%80%9Cunnecessary%2C%E2%80%9D%20saying%20that%20protections%20against%C2%A0caste-based%C2%A0discrimination%C2%A0are%20covered%20legally%20under%20already%20existing%20protections%20that%20%E2%80%9Cshall%20be%20liberally%20construed.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20veto%20created%20an%20uproar%20on%20both%20sides%20of%20the%20South%20Asian%20community%2C%20spurring%20rallies%20at%20the%20capitol%2C%20lobbying%20lines%20through%20hallways%2C%20and%20a%C2%A0hunger%20strike%20in%20favor%20of%20the%20bill.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThose%20opposing%20the%20bill%2C%20such%20as%20the%20Hindu%20American%20Foundation%2C%20called%20it%C2%A0both%20racist%20and%20a%20potential%20%E2%80%9Cconstitutional%20disaster%2C%E2%80%9D%20which%20would%20have%20%E2%80%9Cput%20a%20target%20on%20hundreds%20of%20thousands%20of%20Californians%20simply%20because%20of%20their%20ethnicity%20or%20racial%20identity.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECritics%20of%20Newsom%E2%80%99s%20veto%20decision%20have%20said%20he%20made%20the%20move%C2%A0in%20order%20to%20maintain%20relations%20with%20a%20growing%20Hindu%20voting%20base%2C%20which%20largely%20upholds%20the%20caste%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThrough%20this%20process%2C%20we%20shined%20a%20light%20on%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fcaste-in-the-us-california-lawmakers-try-to-tackle-discrimination%2Fa-65355964%5C%22%3Elong-hidden%20form%20of%20discrimination%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20persists%20across%20multiple%20communities%20in%20California%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Senator%20Aisha%20Wahab%2C%20the%20first%20Muslim%20and%20Afghan%20American%20woman%20elected%20to%20the%20state%20legislature%2C%20and%20the%20author%20of%20the%20bill.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EEfforts%20pick%20up%20steam%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20veto%2C%20Fresno%2C%20a%20city%20in%20California%E2%80%99s%20Central%20Valley%2C%20unanimously%20agreed%20to%20ban%20caste-based%20discrimination%20specifically%C2%A0about%20a%20week%20prior%20to%20the%20veto%20at%20the%20state%20level.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20February%2C%20Seattle%20became%20the%20first%20US%20city%20to%20outlaw%20caste-based%20discrimination.%20Educational%20institutions%2C%20including%20California%20State%20University%2C%20Harvard%2C%20Brandeis%20and%20the%20University%20of%20California%20%E2%80%93%20Davis%2C%20have%20all%20in%20recent%20years%20have%20made%20separate%20legal%20provisions%20on%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20corporate%20world%20has%20also%20added%20to%20the%20movement%2C%20with%20tech%20giants%20including%20Apple%20and%20IBM%20updating%20employee%20policies%20to%20include%20caste%20discrimination%20in%20recent%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThose%20protections%20follow%20a%202020%20lawsuit%20initiated%20by%20the%20California%20Department%20of%20Fair%20Employment%20and%20Housing%20against%20Cisco%2C%20a%20%24195%20billion%20(%E2%82%AC178%20billion)%20company%2C%20on%20the%20grounds%20that%20a%20Dalit%20employee%20had%20been%20severely%20discriminated%20against%20by%20supervisors%20of%20a%20%E2%80%9Chigher%E2%80%9D%20caste.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHad%20caste%20discrimination%20been%20recognized%20then%2C%20advocates%20have%20said%2C%20the%20employee%20could%20have%20won%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20now%2C%20Pariyar%20said%20recent%20legal%20efforts%20have%20united%20the%20Dalit%20community%20and%20others%20fighting%20for%20protections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMany%20more%20cities%20are%20rethinking%20caste%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%20%E2%8